- Rubbish!

176
00:16:16,912 --> 00:16:19,972
Is this all you have? They are all
illiterate girls from the village.

177
00:16:20,044 --> 00:16:23,802
They are beautiful.
- You will find everyone beautiful.

178
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:26,902
I hope you haven't clicked these
photos by wearing the saris yourself.

179
00:16:27,278 --> 00:16:29,775
Why do you think I thought of
getting married again at this age?

180
00:16:30,011 --> 00:16:31,798
I am doubtful about it.

181
00:16:32,030 --> 00:16:34,733
Why? My hairs are white.
Is that the reason?

182
00:16:34,893 --> 00:16:38,582
I might be 55 but my heart
is still as young as 25.

183
00:16:38,610 --> 00:16:41,257
Sir, I know that but...
- What?

184
00:16:41,480 --> 00:16:45,134
I am not getting married for her
to cook for me or get kids.

185
00:16:45,250 --> 00:16:49,209
I am tired of having 6 kids already.

186
00:16:49,446 --> 00:16:52,586
Then why are you getting married?
- Now you are asking!

187
00:16:52,960 --> 00:16:58,149
Let me tell you. The girl who gets
married now, I will get her right here.

188
00:16:58,225 --> 00:17:02,421
I will just stand in front of her
and keep looking at her.

189
00:17:02,491 --> 00:17:04,035
That's it.

190
00:17:04,058 --> 00:17:08,650
I want to keep looking at her
for 24 hours 7 days a week.

191
00:17:08,837 --> 00:17:11,192
How do you think should she be?
- Why don't you tell me?

192
00:17:11,257 --> 00:17:14,774
Useless! You need the eyes for that.

193
00:17:15,391 --> 00:17:18,755
Her face should be like
beauty queen Saira Bano. - Okay.

194
00:17:18,918 --> 00:17:20,751
How should he waist be?
- How?

195
00:17:20,773 --> 00:17:23,457
Crazy fellow, it should be like Helen.
- Helen.

196
00:17:23,508 --> 00:17:26,629
And her walking style...

197
00:17:27,073 --> 00:17:30,895
Just like Vaijanthimala.
I mean to say she should be like..

198
00:17:30,999 --> 00:17:33,120
..Padmini. Go and get her.

199
00:17:33,186 --> 00:17:37,747
But sir, do you think such a
beauty will get married to you?

200
00:17:37,889 --> 00:17:40,019
Do you think she will marry you?

201
00:17:40,836 --> 00:17:46,072
Is there anyone better than me who
can appreciate beauty? - No, sir.

202
00:17:46,477 --> 00:17:47,959
Son!

203
00:17:49,058 --> 00:17:51,994
Where are you?
- I am right here.

204
00:17:52,074 --> 00:17:57,146
