money back right now. - Greetings, sir.

287
00:25:21,037 --> 00:25:23,934
Come, dear.
- I need to talk to you.

288
00:25:24,538 --> 00:25:27,259
Is it?
- Why don't you come in the evening?

289
00:25:27,301 --> 00:25:28,346
You are a strange man!

290
00:25:28,428 --> 00:25:31,208
When the girl has come now then
why call her in the evening?

291
00:25:31,389 --> 00:25:34,473
