why she has come to you.

298
00:25:51,595 --> 00:25:55,736
I won't leave until she leaves.
- Sit down.

299
00:25:58,154 --> 00:25:59,716
Come, dear.

300
00:26:05,451 --> 00:26:07,274
Just what I wanted.

301
00:26:07,653 --> 00:26:09,449
Thanks to you..

302
00:26:09,686 --> 00:26:11,768
..my brother is studying
since so many years.

303
00:26:12,305 --> 00:26:14,649
He is in his final year.

304
00:26:14,959 --> 00:26:19,584
At this point, I need Rs 1000.
I will be grateful.

305
00:26:20,399 --> 00:26:21,259
Why, dear?

306
00:26:21,818 --> 00:26:25,345
As soon as he finishes this year,
will he become a doctor? - Yes.

307
00:26:26,701 --> 00:26:28,015
Oh God!

308
00:26:28,180 --> 00:26:31,813
What is the matter? - What can I say?
I don't have money right now.

309
00:26:32,310 --> 00:26:34,934
What? You don't...

310
00:26:36,514 --> 00:26:40,111
I didn't think of it. I came
here with a lot of expectations.

311
00:26:40,717 --> 00:26:43,148
You have never refused till date.

312
00:26:43,474 --> 00:26:45,700
You used to give it to me
without me asking for it.

313
00:26:45,832 --> 00:26:47,577
I used to, right?
- Yes.

314
00:26:47,758 --> 00:26:49,665
When I had, I used to give it.

315
00:26:50,014 --> 00:26:52,555
Today, I don't have any
then how can I give it?

316
00:26:53,497 --> 00:26:55,741
Sir, why don't you do this?

317
00:26:55,788 --> 00:26:59,904
What? - You used to keep our
house in lease and give me money.

318
00:26:59,965 --> 00:27:03,309
Yes. - Buy that house
and give me the money.

319
00:27:03,356 --> 00:27:07,658
Dear, what do you think I am?
Do you think..

320
00:27:07,845 --> 00:27:10,745
..I gave you money according to the
amount your house is worth of?

321
00:27:10,827 --> 00:27:13,285
You aren't married yet.

322
00:27:13,337 --> 00:27:16,331
You work as a maid in other's house.

323
00:27:16,611 --> 00:27:19,696
You somehow manage to take
care of your mom and sisters.

324
00:27:19,759 --> 00:27:21,680
You are making your
brother study MBBS.

325
00:27:21,822 --> 00:27:24,709
I had helped you because
I saw your qualities.

326
00:27:25,125 --> 00:27:26,667
Listen, do one thing.

327
00:27:26,801 --> 00:27:29,020
You need Rs 1000, right?
- Yes.

328
00:27:29,073 --> 00:27:31,895
I am giving you a
guarantee of Rs 2000.

329
00:27:32,035 --> 00:27:34,355
Try somewhere else.
- What are you saying?

330
00:27:34,557 --> 00:27:35,583
I am telling the right thing.

331
00:27:35,879 --> 00:27:39,046
Nowadays, money is a
huge problem, dear.

332
00:27:56,291 --> 00:27:59,994
What is this, mom?
- Kamla's menstrual cycle has started.

333
00:28:05,349 --> 00:28:08,297
What happened, dear?
- Nothing, mom.

334
00:28:09,309 --> 00:28:10,925
We have faced so many problems.

335
00:28:11,792 --> 00:28:13,360
But I never got scared.

336
00:28:13,973 --> 00:28:16,533
But today after learning about
Kamla's menstrual cycle..

337
00:28:16,935 --> 00:28:19,334
..I don't know why I am getting scared.

338
00:28:19,386 --> 00:28:21,126
What are you saying, dear?

339
00:28:21,418 --> 00:28:23,966
Every girl gets her menstrual
cycle after growing up.

340
00:28:24,034 --> 00:28:25,482
That's true, mom.

341
00:28:26,026 --> 00:28:29,358
Nowadays, a normal girl also
cannot get married easily..

342
00:28:29,555 --> 00:28:31,472
..until a good amount
of dowry is given.

343
00:28:31,892 --> 00:28:35,392
Kamla is poor and dumb as well.

344
00:28:36,034 --> 00:28:40,142
From where will we get dowry
for her, whom will we ask...

345
00:28:42,375 --> 00:28:45,850
Mom, there are 5 more
girls after her.

346
00:28:46,050 --> 00:28:47,941
Every year one of them will
get their menstrual cycle.

347
00:28:48,406 --> 00:28:51,196
From where will we get...
- Parvati.

348
00:28:52,136 --> 00:28:56,635
Shall we go to the market?
- Yes. I was waiting for you. Let's go.

349
00:29:03,164 --> 00:29:06,773
Oh God! The clouds are thundering.

350
00:29:06,933 --> 00:29:08,559
I think it will rain heavily today.

351
00:29:08,646 --> 00:29:11,233
Yes, Parvati.
Look, it's getting darker.

352
00:29:12,990 --> 00:29:16,212
Suresh, you need to buy new
clothes and books, right?

353
00:29:16,358 --> 00:29:18,921
If it starts raining,
everything will be wet.

354
00:29:19,073 --> 00:29:22,665
Yes, that's true.
- Let's go tomorrow.

355
00:29:23,097 --> 00:29:25,299
Okay. We'll go tomorrow.

356
00:30:14,067 --> 00:30:16,927
Parvati, it's you.
I can't believe it.

357
00:30:17,450 --> 00:30:19,978
Come inside, Parvati.
Mom isn't at home.

358
00:30:20,135 --> 00:30:21,543
She has gone to meet her sister.

359
00:30:25,575 --> 00:30:27,636
You are completely drenched.

360
00:30:28,335 --> 00:30:29,558
Here, dry your hair.

361
00:30:30,357 --> 00:30:33,507
What was the need to come alone at
this hour when it's raining outside?

362
00:30:33,723 --> 00:30:35,582
You should've called me,
I would've come.

363
00:30:36,049 --> 00:30:37,542
I don't understand.

364
00:30:37,686 --> 00:30:40,254
What is so important that you
couldn't tell me before?

365
00:30:40,402 --> 00:30:43,214
Or tomorrow morning.
- I was about to come in the evening.

366
00:30:43,662 --> 00:30:46,655
But I was thinking whether
I should come or not.

367
00:30:47,303 --> 00:30:49,177
Then I decided that come what may..

368
00:30:49,555 --> 00:30:51,665
..I must meet you.
That's why I am here.

369
00:30:51,747 --> 00:30:53,643
Anyway, what is the matter?

370
00:30:54,413 --> 00:30:55,465
Tell me.

371
00:30:55,962 --> 00:30:58,700
Don't worry.
Tell me, what is the matter?

372
00:30:59,187 --> 00:31:01,624
Suresh is in his final year.
- Yes.

373
00:31:02,254 --> 00:31:04,181
I was supposed to get
money from somewhere.

374
00:31:04,875 --> 00:31:06,917
But I didn't get anything there.

375
00:31:07,701 --> 00:31:09,852
I need Rs 1000 right now.

376
00:31:10,235 --> 00:31:12,260
Can you give me?
- Parvati.

377
00:31:19,369 --> 00:31:21,843
What happened?
- I am stone-hearted person.

378
00:31:22,335 --> 00:31:25,855
What are you saying?
- Yes, Parvati. Had that not been true..

379
00:31:26,440 --> 00:31:29,595
..then I would've died
by now for not being..

380
00:31:29,734 --> 00:31:31,488
..able to fulfill such a
small demand of yours.

381
00:31:32,035 --> 00:31:33,893
Why are you worried?

382
00:31:34,372 --> 00:31:37,800
It's just me who is asking for it.
No one else.

383
00:31:37,877 --> 00:31:39,561
That's what I feel bad about.

384
00:31:40,218 --> 00:31:42,536
The one who never asked
for anything till date..

385
00:31:43,119 --> 00:31:46,187
..she asked me for something
so small out of helplessness..

386
00:31:46,449 --> 00:31:48,004
..and I couldn't fulfill that.

387
00:31:48,215 --> 00:31:52,490
Listen, I knew that you
wouldn't have money.

388
00:31:53,057 --> 00:31:54,427
Yet, I asked you for it.

389
00:31:55,124 --> 00:31:56,259
Do you know why?

390
00:31:57,056 --> 00:32:00,300
If I am unable to fund
Suresh's studies this year..

391
00:32:00,527 --> 00:32:03,887
..I won't be sad later..

392
00:32:04,147 --> 00:32:05,801
..that I didn't ask
for money from you.

393
00:32:07,155 --> 00:32:08,848
Now I am happy that..

394
00:32:09,151 --> 00:32:11,910
..I tried as much as I could.

395
00:32:12,933 --> 00:32:14,342
That's why I came to you.

396
00:32:15,242 --> 00:32:16,267
Oh my God!

397
00:32:16,721 --> 00:32:18,915
You are suddenly asking
for such a huge amount.

398
00:32:19,388 --> 00:32:21,361
We have a lot of spending ourselves.

399
00:32:21,864 --> 00:32:26,591
You know that ever since a baby is
born, the doctors, the medicines..

400
00:32:26,613 --> 00:32:28,969
..cost so much and people keep coming.

401
00:32:28,992 --> 00:32:31,104
Money is just getting spend.

402
00:32:31,499 --> 00:32:33,027
What do I hide from you?

403
00:32:33,452 --> 00:32:36,918
I was worried as to how to pay
your salary of this month.

404
00:32:38,436 --> 00:32:41,157
Okay, ma'am. I'll take your leave.

405
00:32:43,548 --> 00:32:48,174
I have found such a good groom
that your fate will shine.

406
00:32:48,344 --> 00:32:51,781
His wealth is worth Rs 20,00,000
and hard cash is separate.

407
00:32:51,871 --> 00:32:52,999
I am telling the truth.

408
00:32:53,230 --> 00:32:54,608
The thing is that..

409
00:32:54,630 --> 00:32:58,780
..ever since he has seen your
daughter, he wants to marry her.

410
00:32:58,850 --> 00:33:01,807
That's okay.
But didn't a wealthy groom..

411
00:33:01,966 --> 00:33:05,627
..get a girl from a wealthy family?
- You have asked the right question.

412
00:33:05,839 --> 00:33:08,709
This is his second marriage.
- Second marriage?

413
00:33:08,901 --> 00:33:12,057
Kids?
- He has 6 of them.

414
00:33:12,199 --> 00:33:14,712
What is his age?
- Not much.

415
00:33:14,788 --> 00:33:16,685
He is about 50 years old.

416
00:33:17,113 --> 00:33:19,743
Get up! Get up and leave.

417
00:33:19,795 --> 00:33:23,280
Listen, the person I am
talking to you about..

418
00:33:23,350 --> 00:33:24,894
..at least meet him once.

419
00:33:24,991 --> 00:33:26,161
Enough. I don't want to meet him.

420
00:33:26,239 --> 00:33:29,352
Please leave from here.
- I will ask him to come and meet you.

421
00:33:29,403 --> 00:33:30,566
At least meet him once.

422
00:33:30,629 --> 00:33:33,356
I have told you that
we aren't interested.

423
00:33:33,390 --> 00:33:35,188
Then why are you insisting?

424
00:33:35,226 --> 00:33:36,889
I said, leave right now. Or else...

425
00:33:37,007 --> 00:33:38,469
Alright. As you wish.

426
00:33:42,193 --> 00:33:45,139
Please wait. Please come here.

427
00:33:47,271 --> 00:33:49,405
The person you were talking about..

428
00:33:49,723 --> 00:33:52,733
..can you help us meet?
- Yes, why not?

429
00:33:52,783 --> 00:33:54,927
He is waiting to meet you.

430
00:33:55,210 --> 00:33:56,648
Not to see him.

431
00:33:57,164 --> 00:33:59,423
It is for me to talk to him clearly.

432
00:33:59,821 --> 00:34:01,976
Go and tell him and ask him to come.

433
00:34:02,185 --> 00:34:05,430
Don't send him here.
Ask him to come to the temple at 5pm.

434
00:34:05,849 --> 00:34:08,049
Parvati, why are you calling him?

435
00:34:08,199 --> 00:34:11,720
Why? What's the problem?
- We don't agree to this.

436
00:34:12,572 --> 00:34:15,310
Do you think I do?
- Then why are you calling him?

437
00:34:15,739 --> 00:34:17,289
Am I calling him with
a wedding procession?

438
00:34:17,833 --> 00:34:19,557
First, we'll meet and talk.

439
00:34:20,048 --> 00:34:22,110
I'll talk to him about
whatever possible.

440
00:34:22,506 --> 00:34:26,194
If it works and everyone likes him..

441
00:34:26,607 --> 00:34:28,376
..then we'll think about marriage.

442
00:34:28,458 --> 00:34:31,489
Parvati, there's nothing
to think about in this.

443
00:34:31,698 --> 00:34:32,847
You took the decision!

444
00:34:33,487 --> 00:34:35,642
Please go and ask him to come.
- You won't do that.

445
00:34:35,665 --> 00:34:37,989
I am asking you to do so.
- You go inside.

446
00:34:38,010 --> 00:34:39,350
Parvati.
- Go inside.

447
00:34:39,372 --> 00:34:41,093
Parvati, as long as I am alive...
- Enough...

448
00:34:41,406 --> 00:34:43,763
We are outside the house.
Why are you fighting here?

449
00:34:44,043 --> 00:34:46,046
Let's go inside and talk.
- Parvati, even if I die...

450
00:34:46,128 --> 00:34:47,431
Suresh!

451
00:34:47,656 --> 00:34:50,465
Are you going inside
or should I leave?

452
00:35:01,992 --> 00:35:05,934
What is it, Parvati? What do
you want to talk to him about?

453
00:35:06,016 --> 00:35:07,883
Ask me about it, mom.

454
00:35:08,070 --> 00:35:10,173
I'll tell you what she wants
to talk to him about.

455
00:35:10,196 --> 00:35:13,580
Tell me. - You will be asking
him to help me in my studies.

456
00:35:13,734 --> 00:35:16,786
You will ask him to take care
of your family. Right? - Yes.

457
00:35:17,077 --> 00:35:20,207
That means you are pushing
yourself in to hell.

458
00:35:20,622 --> 00:35:23,592
Am I in heaven living
a peaceful life now?

459
00:35:24,828 --> 00:35:26,424
You are right, dear.

460
00:35:27,219 --> 00:35:30,333
You never got peace in the
house you were born in.

461
00:35:31,113 --> 00:35:34,088
I wish you get peace in your
husband's house at least.

462
00:35:34,553 --> 00:35:37,485
That is what I am saying, mom.
Did you hear?

463
00:35:37,844 --> 00:35:41,956
He is a rich man.
- Whatever it is. I won't let this happen.

464
00:35:42,082 --> 00:35:44,125
Reason?
- What's his age?

465
00:35:44,650 --> 00:35:48,454
What is your age?
Tell me, what is your age?

466
00:35:49,402 --> 00:35:52,246
Had you got married
at the right time..

467
00:35:52,470 --> 00:35:54,784
..then you would've been a
father of three kids.

468
00:35:55,022 --> 00:35:56,880
And I am your elder sister.

469
00:35:57,202 --> 00:35:59,726
Go and get a man of my age.

470
00:35:59,795 --> 00:36:01,499
Alright, I will get.

471
00:36:01,580 --> 00:36:03,619
Why are you yelling
without knowing anything?

472
00:36:03,742 --> 00:36:07,137
I am not yelling. I am telling
the truth. I swear I will do it.

473
00:36:07,213 --> 00:36:09,397
First, do it then I will see.

474
00:36:09,792 --> 00:36:13,118
Stupid. You are studying in college.

475
00:36:13,448 --> 00:36:18,007
Nowadays, when a 40-year old man
looks at a 20-year old girl, he says..

476
00:36:18,070 --> 00:36:19,221
..that she is way too old.

477
00:36:19,334 --> 00:36:22,814
And he thinks he will
get a man of my age.

478
00:36:22,997 --> 00:36:25,465
I am 28 years old right now.

479
00:36:25,514 --> 00:36:28,480
Parvati, I am saying
this out of sadness.

480
00:36:28,589 --> 00:36:31,630
You are trying to shut
me by saying all this.

481
00:36:31,711 --> 00:36:34,960
I beg of you.
This marriage shouldn't happen.

482
00:36:35,059 --> 00:36:36,631
I won't let it happen.

483
00:36:36,728 --> 00:36:40,971
Yes, dear. It would be better to stay
alone then get married like this.

484
00:36:41,169 --> 00:36:43,887
That's right. Suresh?

485
00:36:44,050 --> 00:36:46,976
Mom is right.
- I see.

486
00:36:47,541 --> 00:36:49,000
I'll stay unmarried then.

487
00:36:49,212 --> 00:36:51,142
Let's decide right now.

488
00:36:51,697 --> 00:36:55,129
That means if I get married and go..

489
00:36:55,393 --> 00:36:57,288
..then none of you
will be able to eat.

490
00:36:57,734 --> 00:37:01,546
For your comfort, I should keep
working as a maid all my life.

491
00:37:01,731 --> 00:37:04,533
And then one day I will die.

492
00:37:04,882 --> 00:37:08,741
This is what you want.
Fine, I will do this.

493
00:37:08,916 --> 00:37:10,521
What are you saying, Parvati?

494
00:37:10,573 --> 00:37:13,677
When I said that I should leave
my studies and work somewhere..

495
00:37:13,759 --> 00:37:17,177
..you refused. You asked me
to study and become a doctor.

496
00:37:17,348 --> 00:37:21,487
Now you are accusing me.
- I am making you study. Is it for me?

497
00:37:21,576 --> 00:37:22,601
Then for whom?

498
00:37:23,503 --> 00:37:27,814
Kamla is dumb.
There are more 5 sisters you have.

499
00:37:28,208 --> 00:37:31,139
I am making you study so
that they get married..

500
00:37:31,451 --> 00:37:35,177
..in a better place.
- But Parvati, even you are my sister.

501
00:37:35,319 --> 00:37:36,840
Do you think I won't
take care of you?

502
00:37:37,715 --> 00:37:39,981
God knows whether I
will be alive by then.

503
00:37:40,066 --> 00:37:41,921
What are you saying, Parvati?
- Keep quiet.

504
00:37:42,465 --> 00:37:46,805
You think after your studies, people
will come running to you with money.

505
00:37:47,071 --> 00:37:51,016
After that you will have to work
hard and make a name for yourself.

506
00:37:51,113 --> 00:37:53,048
Only after that will
your earnings begin.

507
00:37:53,327 --> 00:37:55,069
Once you start earning,

508
00:37:55,452 --> 00:37:57,730
God knows if you will
take care of us.

509
00:37:57,943 --> 00:38:00,336
Parvati.
- I know there are barely any brothers..

510
00:38:00,485 --> 00:38:02,484
..who take care of their sisters.

511
00:38:02,646 --> 00:38:06,738
After marriage, they take
care of their wife and kids.

512
00:38:06,900 --> 00:38:08,843
Who takes care of their
parents or sisters?

513
00:38:08,865 --> 00:38:11,465
Parvati, I know there
are brothers like that.

514
00:38:11,571 --> 00:38:16,169
But their sisters are
not goddesses like you.

515
00:38:16,307 --> 00:38:19,552
I just know you and
your sacrifices.

516
00:38:19,746 --> 00:38:22,256
Parvati, after all
I am your brother.

517
00:38:22,425 --> 00:38:25,383
Your feeling of sacrifices
can be in me as well.

518
00:38:25,579 --> 00:38:30,791
I see. That's great. So you are
also ready to make sacrifices.

519
00:38:30,843 --> 00:38:32,783
Why not?
- Do you promise?

520
00:38:32,914 --> 00:38:38,919
I promise. - Then promise me that
unless you get all your sisters married..

521
00:38:39,155 --> 00:38:40,998
..you won't get married.

522
00:38:41,080 --> 00:38:43,629
I won't promise that
I won't get married.

523
00:38:43,759 --> 00:38:47,681
I promise that unless I get
all my sisters married..

524
00:38:47,718 --> 00:38:49,891
..I won't think about getting married.

525
00:38:49,990 --> 00:38:52,917
So, to get these 6 sisters
married in a good family..

526
00:38:53,069 --> 00:38:55,879
..you will have to become a doctor
first. - Yes, Parvati.

527
00:38:56,243 --> 00:38:58,998
Then to make you a doctor,
I will have to get married.

528
00:38:59,021 --> 00:39:02,052
Parvati. Parvati, we will
find another way for that.

529
00:39:02,168 --> 00:39:03,840
I will complete my studies somehow.

530
00:39:03,940 --> 00:39:05,816
You won't be able to do it, Suresh.
You won't be able to.

531
00:39:05,898 --> 00:39:07,211
Let me try it.

532
00:39:07,293 --> 00:39:10,467
Suresh, you don't understand the
world. This is not possible.

533
00:39:10,538 --> 00:39:13,184
Parvati, what are you talking about?

534
00:39:13,235 --> 00:39:15,185
Alright, forget about the world.

535
00:39:15,641 --> 00:39:18,224
Do you know what's the
condition in our house? - What?

536
00:39:18,448 --> 00:39:20,440
The entire house is mortgaged.

537
00:39:22,151 --> 00:39:26,201
Suresh, the day you
started studying MBBS..

538
00:39:26,479 --> 00:39:28,820
..I had to keep this house mortgage.

539
00:39:29,081 --> 00:39:31,904
Did I ever tell you about it?

540
00:39:32,498 --> 00:39:35,493
We have faced so many problems.

541
00:39:35,634 --> 00:39:38,810
But did I ever show it to you?

542
00:39:39,405 --> 00:39:41,426
Today, I am saying it. Why?

543
00:39:41,745 --> 00:39:44,006
Because I have nothing today.

544
00:39:44,615 --> 00:39:46,677
I am completely helpless.

545
00:39:46,957 --> 00:39:49,770
The money lender might
just come someday..

546
00:39:50,168 --> 00:39:52,692
..and throw us out of the house.

547
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:55,349
I think of it and get so afraid.

548
00:39:55,749 --> 00:39:58,022
I met everyone possible.

549
00:39:58,328 --> 00:40:00,957
I asked for money from
everyone possible.

550
00:40:01,257 --> 00:40:03,857
I begged everyone I could.

551
00:40:04,140 --> 00:40:09,955
But when I saw that there is no other way,
there's nothing we can do..

552
00:40:10,044 --> 00:40:12,668
..that's when I decided to do this.

553
00:40:12,957 --> 00:40:16,778
Go away. Let me be in my situation.

554
00:40:20,536 --> 00:40:21,724
Greetings, sir.

555
00:40:21,930 --> 00:40:26,214
Come. I thought you forgot that
there's a case you are fighting.

556
00:40:26,348 --> 00:40:28,494
Why? I keep coming.

557
00:40:28,648 --> 00:40:31,737
How will that help? Sit down.

558
00:40:33,172 --> 00:40:37,611
Look, your case is very complicated.
Opponent is very strong.

559
00:40:37,845 --> 00:40:42,224
I have left all my work aside and
I am concentrating on your case.

560
00:40:42,467 --> 00:40:45,252
You come every time but you
need to pay the fees as well.

561
00:40:45,273 --> 00:40:48,283
Last week, I had given you Rs 300.

562
00:40:48,483 --> 00:40:50,609
That's it! Is the case over?

563
00:40:50,690 --> 00:40:54,111
Right. I will try to give you more.

564
00:40:54,579 --> 00:40:57,519
But please tell me about
the progress of the case.

565
00:40:57,602 --> 00:41:00,825
I have already told you, the
opponent is very strong.

566
00:41:00,985 --> 00:41:02,698
Your side is weak.

567
00:41:03,076 --> 00:41:07,027
I will make points and
present it in court.

568
00:41:07,173 --> 00:41:09,448
Whether you win or lose,
it is dependent on that.

569
00:41:09,664 --> 00:41:11,580
Go and arrange for the fees.

570
00:41:15,867 --> 00:41:17,183
Goodbye.
- Goodbye.

571
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:23,131
Sir, is his case really weak?

572
00:41:23,239 --> 00:41:25,490
Who said?
- You said.

573
00:41:26,866 --> 00:41:30,836
Stupid fellow, our case is very strong.
We will surely win.

574
00:41:31,295 --> 00:41:33,392
But after winning the case,

575
00:41:33,419 --> 00:41:36,410
I don't want to file a case
on anyone to get my fees.

576
00:41:36,532 --> 00:41:37,704
Understood?

577
00:41:45,326 --> 00:41:50,381
So, we have been waiting for the girl since
such a long time. Where is the girl?

578
00:41:50,529 --> 00:41:56,558
I had told you that the
girl has called you at 5pm.

579
00:41:56,637 --> 00:41:59,962
But you left home at 3pm
and have been sitting here..

580
00:42:00,102 --> 00:42:02,515
..then what can she do
and what can I do.

581
00:42:02,782 --> 00:42:05,932
When the girl has a house of her own..

582
00:42:06,039 --> 00:42:08,166
..then why did she call
us in the temple?

583
00:42:08,218 --> 00:42:13,779
I think that her brother and mother
don't want this marriage to happen.

584
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:17,104
Forget about them.
What about the girl?

585
00:42:17,155 --> 00:42:20,721
Sir, had she not been interested
why would she call you?

586
00:42:20,773 --> 00:42:22,316
Yes, that's right.

587
00:42:22,552 --> 00:42:24,999
There she is. She has come.
- Go. Go from here.

588
00:42:25,043 --> 00:42:26,126
Wait a moment.

589
00:42:26,530 --> 00:42:29,198
Let me introduce you.
- Come, dear.

590
00:42:29,281 --> 00:42:31,736
He is the one who
wants to marry you.

591
00:42:31,858 --> 00:42:33,863
I have seen him.
- Right.

592
00:42:33,982 --> 00:42:37,004
We have met each other.
You can leave.

593
00:42:37,597 --> 00:42:39,009
Tell me, what is the matter?

594
00:42:39,662 --> 00:42:42,437
Come. We will speak in
front of God's idol.

595
00:42:42,487 --> 00:42:45,302
Yes, let's go. We will talk here.

596
00:42:48,575 --> 00:42:52,777
What I wish to say is a big thing.
- Surely, tell me.

597
00:42:52,973 --> 00:42:55,927
That's why I wish to keep
someone has witness.

598
00:42:56,005 --> 00:42:59,916
Is it? If you wish, I can get the
richest people of the town here.

599
00:42:59,990 --> 00:43:01,412
That's not needed.

600
00:43:02,268 --> 00:43:08,026
It is better to keep God
as the witness and talk.

601
00:43:08,102 --> 00:43:12,642
Of course it is. I am a huge devotee.
I see God in everything.

602
00:43:12,847 --> 00:43:16,882
In the stone, in the wall,
in the pillar, in you and me.

603
00:43:17,075 --> 00:43:19,676
Anyway, forget that.
Tell me, what were you about to say.

604
00:43:19,728 --> 00:43:21,527
Tell me, what your demands are.

605
00:43:21,651 --> 00:43:25,537
I wish that my brother completes his
final year of studies. - MBBS, right?

606
00:43:26,086 --> 00:43:28,453
Yes. He is in his final year.

607
00:43:28,545 --> 00:43:34,739
No problem. Even he fails, I will
use my contacts and get him passed.

608
00:43:34,887 --> 00:43:38,500
No. That's not needed.
He is very intelligent.

609
00:43:38,892 --> 00:43:41,421
You can just help with money.

610
00:43:41,805 --> 00:43:43,578
He will surely pass.

611
00:43:43,721 --> 00:43:47,495
Alright. I will do it. But he
should be at my house to study.

612
00:43:47,533 --> 00:43:49,288
Demand No. 2.

613
00:43:49,480 --> 00:43:52,119
Until he becomes a doctor
and starts earning..

614
00:43:52,613 --> 00:43:56,391
..the responsibility of my
family will be on you.

615
00:43:56,559 --> 00:43:58,252
This is what I am sad about.

616
00:43:58,338 --> 00:44:00,579
You are still differentiating.

617
00:44:00,598 --> 00:44:04,328
Both of us are one.
They are my family too.

618
00:44:04,774 --> 00:44:08,769
Okay, you will take the
responsibility of our family right?

619
00:44:08,976 --> 00:44:13,616
I swear on God,
on myself and on you.

620
00:44:13,693 --> 00:44:16,439
I will take care of our family.

621
00:44:16,542 --> 00:44:18,918
I too swear on God..

622
00:44:19,379 --> 00:44:23,079
..that I am happily
ready to marry you.

623
00:44:23,378 --> 00:44:26,894
That's great. Take this.

624
00:44:27,098 --> 00:44:28,347
Why do I need so much?

625
00:44:29,079 --> 00:44:30,124
Rs 1000 is enough.

626
00:44:30,256 --> 00:44:33,129
Keep it. Why are you
counting unnecessarily?

627
00:44:33,365 --> 00:44:34,337
All this is yours.

628
00:44:34,474 --> 00:44:38,141
The keys of the house will be with
you then you can do what you want.

629
00:44:38,250 --> 00:44:42,294
One important thing. No one should
know that we are getting married.

630
00:44:43,258 --> 00:44:45,515
Why?
- Well, my mom..

631
00:44:45,615 --> 00:44:49,766
..wants me to get married to someone
else and I don't like those girls.

632
00:44:49,824 --> 00:44:53,142
I really like you. So this
shouldn't be revealed.

633
00:44:53,204 --> 00:44:55,559
If my brother learns about it then..

634
00:44:55,649 --> 00:44:57,816
..he will put a stay
order on the marriage.

635
00:44:57,890 --> 00:45:00,602
We will get married next
Friday here itself.

636
00:45:00,990 --> 00:45:04,933
Okay. I'll take your leave.
- Go on.

637
00:45:07,072 --> 00:45:08,211
Parvati.

638
00:45:18,333 --> 00:45:22,714
Parvati, you have taken
the right decision.

639
00:45:23,387 --> 00:45:24,746
The ones who have a heart..

640
00:45:25,390 --> 00:45:27,925
..will surely appreciate
your decision.

641
00:45:28,469 --> 00:45:31,925
This is a decision which
tells the whole world..

642
00:45:32,525 --> 00:45:36,455
..that a poor person's heart
doesn't belong to him.

643
00:45:37,582 --> 00:45:39,384
But the poverty belongs to them.

644
00:45:40,268 --> 00:45:44,073
Yes, Parvati.
Today, I have come to the temple.

645
00:45:45,242 --> 00:45:47,220
I have heard your conversation.

646
00:45:48,515 --> 00:45:52,084
What do you have to say about it?

647
00:45:52,301 --> 00:45:55,639
What can I say? I am sure..

648
00:45:56,579 --> 00:45:59,364
..that you do love me..

649
00:45:59,881 --> 00:46:02,814
..but you love your family more.

650
00:46:03,902 --> 00:46:05,593
I am telling the truth, Parvati.

651
00:46:06,172 --> 00:46:07,813
I decided yesterday..

652
00:46:08,443 --> 00:46:10,810
..that the two of us can
never get married.

653
00:46:11,389 --> 00:46:14,723
Don't think that I am saying this..

654
00:46:15,483 --> 00:46:16,879
..because you are away from me.

655
00:46:18,240 --> 00:46:20,501
I was expecting that I
will get the wealth back.

656
00:46:20,980 --> 00:46:26,415
Over this expectation I wanted to take
care of you, your family and Suresh.

657
00:46:26,686 --> 00:46:29,695
But yesterday my lawyer told me..

658
00:46:30,182 --> 00:46:31,936
..that my case is very weak.

659
00:46:32,560 --> 00:46:34,769
I feel I will lose this case.

660
00:46:35,816 --> 00:46:38,012
If I get married to you
in such a situation..

661
00:46:38,344 --> 00:46:40,419
..then it will be a disaster.

662
00:46:41,414 --> 00:46:46,374
Parvati, the sacrifice you made
for your brother and sisters..

663
00:46:46,628 --> 00:46:47,971
..it's a huge sacrifice.

664
00:46:48,536 --> 00:46:51,633
I hope this sacrifice of yours
keeps you in peace always.

665
00:46:52,155 --> 00:46:53,275
I'll take your leave.

666
00:46:54,049 --> 00:46:55,382
Listen.

667
00:46:57,009 --> 00:46:58,611
Will you agree to something I say?

668
00:46:59,087 --> 00:47:04,014
Tell me, Parvati. - You want me
to be happy and in peace.

669
00:47:04,553 --> 00:47:06,163
Then do one thing for me.

670
00:47:07,196 --> 00:47:09,285
You should get married..

671
00:47:09,897 --> 00:47:12,880
..and bring your bride
to visit my house.

672
00:47:14,712 --> 00:47:15,816
I will try.

673
00:47:18,093 --> 00:47:19,499
I will try, Parvati.

674
00:47:37,324 --> 00:47:41,377
Alright. I am married now.
Go and inform my family about it.

675
00:47:43,158 --> 00:47:45,301
Give it to him.
- No, I won't.

676
00:47:45,353 --> 00:47:48,035
You won't! You are very stubborn.
Give it!

677
00:47:48,369 --> 00:47:50,802
Take it. Monsters!
- You called me a monster!

678
00:47:50,868 --> 00:47:52,931
Why? Why? Why? Why?

679
00:47:52,983 --> 00:47:54,791
Oh God! The kids are impossible!

680
00:47:54,814 --> 00:47:57,266
Ratan, you are here
at the right time.

681
00:47:57,429 --> 00:47:58,967
Please talk to them.

682
00:47:59,031 --> 00:48:02,277
Mom, kids are mischievous.
Why are you getting mad at them?

683
00:48:02,329 --> 00:48:03,851
Are they kids? Really?
- Of course.

684
00:48:04,056 --> 00:48:06,787
Ma'am, what's going on?

685
00:48:07,109 --> 00:48:08,399
Are you playing with the kids?

686
00:48:08,435 --> 00:48:11,384
I am going crazy and you
think I am playing!

687
00:48:11,466 --> 00:48:14,059
Ma'am, you don't have
to worry at all.

688
00:48:14,341 --> 00:48:17,384
After your daughter-in-law comes,
everything will be fine. - What?

689
00:48:17,941 --> 00:48:18,804
What are you saying?

690
00:48:18,856 --> 00:48:22,381
Ma'am, your son's wife will be
your daughter-in-law, right?

691
00:48:22,577 --> 00:48:24,593
What do you mean?
- Hey!

692
00:48:24,835 --> 00:48:26,726
What are you talking about?
Tell me clearly.

693
00:48:26,778 --> 00:48:28,580
Sir, don't you know.

694
00:48:28,603 --> 00:48:31,985
Today in the morning,
Manoharlal got married again.

695
00:48:32,077 --> 00:48:33,797
What are you saying?
- When did that happen?

696
00:48:33,855 --> 00:48:35,263
What do we do now, Ratan?

697
00:48:35,502 --> 00:48:38,764
He has made such a huge mistake.
- Wait, mom.

698
00:48:39,386 --> 00:48:40,990
Hey, you pigeon.
- I am a man, sir.

699
00:48:41,072 --> 00:48:42,098
I know.

700
00:48:42,179 --> 00:48:44,419
What nonsense is this?
- I am telling the truth.

701
00:48:44,514 --> 00:48:48,788
I had heard that your elder brother got
married in the temple in the morning.

702
00:48:49,015 --> 00:48:52,478
You have heard!
- You heard! What is this?

703
00:48:53,275 --> 00:48:56,234
A sweet! That means you were
a part of this wedding.

704
00:48:56,291 --> 00:48:58,760
Sir, one should be going to
the wedding of the near ones.

705
00:48:58,902 --> 00:49:02,196
So, you got them married.
- Only God takes these decision, sir.

706
00:49:02,277 --> 00:49:04,457
I am just a medium.
- Idiot!

707
00:49:04,551 --> 00:49:06,712
You got the girl.
You got him married.

708
00:49:06,794 --> 00:49:08,316
And now you have come
here to inform us.

709
00:49:08,464 --> 00:49:12,230
Idiot, he is a father of 6 kids.
Why did you have mess his life?

710
00:49:12,411 --> 00:49:14,410
A person like you shouldn't
be allowed here.

711
00:49:14,588 --> 00:49:16,744
C'mon! Move! Out! Out!

712
00:49:16,796 --> 00:49:20,629
Get out! Get out!
- I am going! I am going!

713
00:49:22,193 --> 00:49:25,104
What is all this, Ratan?
- What a mess this is!

714
00:49:25,210 --> 00:49:28,445
Why do you ask me, mom? Has he ever
done anything right till date?

715
00:49:28,565 --> 00:49:31,081
Oh God! What do I do now?

716
00:49:31,457 --> 00:49:34,955
These kids are without a mother.
I took care of them.

717
00:49:35,068 --> 00:49:37,590
I have taken such good care of them.

718
00:49:37,612 --> 00:49:42,092
The witch that comes, God knows
how she will treat them.

719
00:49:42,185 --> 00:49:43,987
Grandma, who is coming?

720
00:49:44,033 --> 00:49:46,580
Your step mother is coming.

721
00:49:46,662 --> 00:49:48,980
Step-mom! How will she be?

722
00:49:49,092 --> 00:49:50,363
She will be like a cat.

723
00:49:50,571 --> 00:49:52,214
She will punish you all.

724
00:49:52,416 --> 00:49:54,891
She will scare all of you.

725
00:49:56,647 --> 00:49:58,371
There he is!

726
00:50:02,610 --> 00:50:05,266
Wait! Where are you going?

727
00:50:06,688 --> 00:50:09,453
Are you deaf? I am talking to you!

728
00:50:09,475 --> 00:50:12,232
Mr. Groom!
- Did you see that? He stopped.

729
00:50:12,484 --> 00:50:14,925
He just got married.
- Hey, cabbie, you shut up.

730
00:50:14,952 --> 00:50:19,478
Why are you shouting at him?
- How dare you get married again?

731
00:50:19,690 --> 00:50:23,619
If you wanted to get married, why
didn't you wait till my death?

732
00:50:23,877 --> 00:50:27,884
Mom, people say that I am
already aged to get married.

733
00:50:27,948 --> 00:50:31,175
Had I waited for you to die,
I would've been more late.

734
00:50:31,295 --> 00:50:34,934
Shameless! It is a sin
to see your face!

735
00:50:35,016 --> 00:50:37,783
We know what is a sin and a deed.
What does he know?

736
00:50:37,858 --> 00:50:40,883
Did you see how my younger
brother talks to me?

737
00:50:40,957 --> 00:50:44,598
The kind of things you do being
the elder brother is worth that.

738
00:50:44,650 --> 00:50:46,652
You are a father to 6 kids
and you got married again!

739
00:50:46,753 --> 00:50:50,147
Yes, I did that. It's my wish.
You shut up or leave from here.

740
00:50:50,268 --> 00:50:53,654
Who wants to come here anyway?
- Why are standing then? Leave!

741
00:50:53,675 --> 00:50:56,379
I am leaving.
I don't live on your money.

742
00:50:56,491 --> 00:50:58,941
I am capable enough to
take care of myself.

743
00:50:59,054 --> 00:51:00,845
Mom, I'll take your leave.

744
00:51:00,897 --> 00:51:03,232
Ratan. Ratan!
- Let him go.

745
00:51:03,358 --> 00:51:05,271
What else can he do?

746
00:51:05,294 --> 00:51:07,498
Who would want to stay
in a sinner's house?

747
00:51:07,581 --> 00:51:09,676
Asha, your sister-in-law is
coming tomorrow morning.

748
00:51:09,749 --> 00:51:11,723
She must be welcomed properly.

749
00:51:12,260 --> 00:51:15,666
Mom. - What are you telling me?
I have heard everything.

750
00:51:21,800 --> 00:51:24,892
Grandma, why have these people come?

751
00:51:24,970 --> 00:51:29,585
Son, your dad has got
married at this age.

752
00:51:29,645 --> 00:51:31,927
Your step-mom is coming.

753
00:51:32,079 --> 00:51:35,182
We have to welcome her properly.

754
00:51:35,360 --> 00:51:39,134
Why, grandma? You were saying
that she will attack us like a cat.

755
00:51:39,207 --> 00:51:41,210
Is she like that?
- Yes.

756
00:51:41,262 --> 00:51:45,428
You said she will scare us out.
Is she like that?

757
00:51:45,559 --> 00:51:48,486
Yes. That's right.
That's how step-mom's are.

758
00:51:48,687 --> 00:51:53,047
Listen kids, if you tried to
do be mischievous with her..

759
00:51:53,129 --> 00:51:59,171
..the way you are with me then she
will throw you out within no time.

760
00:51:59,253 --> 00:52:00,666
Be careful.

761
00:52:00,839 --> 00:52:03,319
Asha, listen to me carefully.

762
00:52:03,564 --> 00:52:07,518
The second wife is always thinking..

763
00:52:07,831 --> 00:52:10,861
..about her targets to
fight and argue with.

764
00:52:10,980 --> 00:52:12,637
Don't give her a chance.

765
00:52:12,779 --> 00:52:16,954
If the two of you have an
argument then you are loss.

766
00:52:17,873 --> 00:52:19,736
I think she has come. Go on.

767
00:52:46,505 --> 00:52:47,786
Be happy.

768
00:52:59,980 --> 00:53:02,696
Parvati, what are you looking at?

769
00:53:03,023 --> 00:53:05,128
I heard he has 6 kids.

770
00:53:05,689 --> 00:53:07,589
I am unable to see any of them.

771
00:53:44,220 --> 00:53:47,428
Greetings. Do you work her as a maid?
- Yes.

772
00:53:47,694 --> 00:53:50,383
These things are in such a mess.

773
00:53:50,822 --> 00:53:53,388
Don't you think we should clear it?
- Yes.

774
00:53:55,754 --> 00:53:56,937
Please keep it there.

775
00:54:17,511 --> 00:54:18,470
Hey.

776
00:54:20,029 --> 00:54:23,014
She is our step-mom.
She will beat us up.

777
00:54:27,357 --> 00:54:30,091
What's so great about it?
She is smiling!

778
00:54:33,836 --> 00:54:36,365
Oh God! These kids!

779
00:54:53,437 --> 00:54:54,718
Oh no!

780
00:55:10,537 --> 00:55:14,944
Oh! That's not the way you should make
a child drink milk, she might choke.

781
00:55:15,483 --> 00:55:19,957
The head should always be up
while making her drink milk.

782
00:55:29,372 --> 00:55:32,756
Here you go. Make her sleep now.

783
00:55:32,839 --> 00:55:34,841
C'mon, let's go and make you sleep.

784
00:55:39,228 --> 00:55:44,805
No. No. Don't cry. Go to sleep.
Sleep. No.

785
00:55:44,827 --> 00:55:47,098
If you make her sleep like this,
she won't sleep.

786
00:55:47,345 --> 00:55:49,637
If you sing a lullaby,
she will sleep quickly.

787
00:55:49,675 --> 00:55:52,420
Parvati, I don't know any lullaby.

788
00:55:53,575 --> 00:55:55,975
Do women need to learn a lullaby?

789
00:55:57,327 --> 00:55:58,869
The life of a woman..

790
00:55:59,801 --> 00:56:01,327
..itself is a lullaby.

791
00:56:02,671 --> 00:56:10,118
"Go to sleep, my dear girl."

792
00:56:10,783 --> 00:56:16,645
"Why sacrifice your sleep?"

793
00:56:17,602 --> 00:56:24,457
"After this phase of childhood
is gone.."

794
00:56:24,950 --> 00:56:31,018
"..a woman doesn't sleep all her life."

795
00:56:47,209 --> 00:56:57,982
"A woman's life is like a swing,
at this end and at that end."

796
00:56:59,689 --> 00:57:09,366
"A woman's life is like a swing,
at this end and at that end."

797
00:57:09,525 --> 00:57:19,098
"Sometimes there's smile on her face,
sometimes tears rolling down her eyes."

798
00:57:19,241 --> 00:57:29,561
"A woman's life is like a swing,
at this end and at that end."

799
00:57:52,408 --> 00:57:57,368
"She gives such a lot
of peace to the world."

800
00:57:57,390 --> 00:58:02,582
"She does that being a mother,
a sister and a wife."

801
00:58:06,648 --> 00:58:11,213
"She gives such a lot
of peace to the world."

802
00:58:11,410 --> 00:58:16,016
"She does that being a mother,
a sister and a wife."

803
00:58:16,115 --> 00:58:20,726
"Her life is a difficult one."

804
00:58:20,810 --> 00:58:25,947
"The society has never
understood this."

805
00:59:19,956 --> 00:59:21,142
Parvati.

806
00:59:54,061 --> 00:59:56,614
Look, Grandma said the right thing.

807
00:59:56,851 --> 00:59:59,681
Step-mom is going to
scare us with that.

808
00:59:59,824 --> 01:00:03,989
Oh God! Run! Run!
- Run! Run!

809
01:00:06,201 --> 01:00:09,215
Oh God! What is wrong with you!

810
01:00:09,269 --> 01:00:12,735
All of you are such a mess.
You are always troubling me.

811
01:00:12,967 --> 01:00:17,155
Just wait and watch.
I won't spare you.

812
01:00:17,773 --> 01:00:22,543
They have become very mischievous.
I won't spare them today.

813
01:00:24,805 --> 01:00:27,554
Wait! Where are you going?

814
01:00:27,854 --> 01:00:30,547
C'mon! Come here!

815
01:00:30,983 --> 01:00:34,736
Sit down all of you. Sit down!

816
01:00:34,818 --> 01:00:36,407
Mother! Mother!

817
01:00:36,677 --> 01:00:39,862
What are you doing? Leave it.
What is this?

818
01:00:40,622 --> 01:00:42,897
What if they are hurt with this?

819
01:00:43,230 --> 01:00:44,931
You come here. Come here.

820
01:00:45,838 --> 01:00:49,694
Do you think I will
hurt them with this?

821
01:00:49,817 --> 01:00:52,750
I was just trying to scare them.

822
01:00:52,970 --> 01:00:56,413
With a burning wood stick!
There are other ways to scare also.

823
01:00:56,460 --> 01:00:58,556
You don't know this
mischievous bunch.

824
01:00:58,667 --> 01:01:00,762
They are so stubborn,
they won't listen.

825
01:01:00,844 --> 01:01:05,418
That's alright, mother. But please
don't show them the burning stick.

826
01:01:05,853 --> 01:01:08,466
They are raw mud.

827
01:01:08,798 --> 01:01:11,121
The way we mold them,
they will take that shape.

828
01:01:11,736 --> 01:01:13,421
Is this the right way to scare them?

829
01:01:13,522 --> 01:01:15,158
Well, it isn't right.

830
01:01:15,438 --> 01:01:17,957
Then you take care
of them from now on.

831
01:01:18,032 --> 01:01:20,079
I won't come in between.

832
01:01:20,161 --> 01:01:21,355
I am going.

833
01:01:23,048 --> 01:01:25,093
Go. Go and play.

834
01:01:26,176 --> 01:01:27,384
Munni.

835
01:01:28,663 --> 01:01:32,503
Hey, this step-mom is really nice.
She won't scare us.

836
01:01:32,627 --> 01:01:34,929
Grandma lied to us.

837
01:01:34,981 --> 01:01:38,199
Come. Let's go and ask her.
- Yes, let's go.

838
01:01:39,508 --> 01:01:41,382
Come. Come here.

839
01:01:43,376 --> 01:01:44,776
Why are you standing there?

840
01:01:45,751 --> 01:01:46,892
What do you want?

841
01:01:46,957 --> 01:01:48,954
We'll tell you, step-mom.

842
01:01:49,205 --> 01:01:51,920
Don't call me that. Call me 'mom'.

843
01:01:52,042 --> 01:01:55,150
Mom, will you scare us like a cat?

844
01:01:55,253 --> 01:01:59,791
What?
- No, son, I will never hurt you.

845
01:02:00,030 --> 01:02:02,995
Will you hurt us with
a burning stick?

846
01:02:03,102 --> 01:02:07,817
Why do you say so? When grandma was
showing the stick, I snatched it.

847
01:02:08,200 --> 01:02:09,490
Hey, listen.

848
01:02:09,820 --> 01:02:11,947
Alright. Now go and play. Go.

849
01:02:13,714 --> 01:02:15,595
We hate!
- Grandma!

850
01:02:15,677 --> 01:02:17,377
We hate!
- Grandma!

851
01:02:17,400 --> 01:02:19,088
We hate!
- Grandma!

852
01:02:19,170 --> 01:02:21,856
Dear Lord! What's wrong
with all of you?

853
01:02:21,979 --> 01:02:23,786
Why do you hate me?

854
01:02:23,884 --> 01:02:27,991
Grandma, you lied to us that
mom is hurt us like a cat.

855
01:02:28,090 --> 01:02:31,290
Mom is really nice. She loves us.
You are a witch.

856
01:02:31,384 --> 01:02:35,555
You hurt us like a cat.
You scared us with a burning stick.

857
01:02:35,632 --> 01:02:38,538
Come. Let's beat her up.

858
01:02:40,283 --> 01:02:44,437
Hey! Stop it! - What is all this?
You are beating up your grandma!

859
01:02:44,626 --> 01:02:46,302
This is wrong. Why did you do this?

860
01:02:46,550 --> 01:02:51,261
What happened, mother?
- Parvati, before you came..

861
01:02:51,409 --> 01:02:54,588
..I had told them something about you.
- What did you say?

862
01:02:54,708 --> 01:02:59,160
Usually, step-moms
are bad in nature.

863
01:02:59,407 --> 01:03:03,599
So I told them that you
will hurt them like cats..

864
01:03:03,705 --> 01:03:05,496
..and scare you with a burning stick.

865
01:03:05,664 --> 01:03:08,782
Ever since you have come,
they are observing you.

866
01:03:08,864 --> 01:03:11,998
They love you a lot.
They were saying..

867
01:03:12,078 --> 01:03:14,864
..that you are really
nice and I am witch.

868
01:03:14,946 --> 01:03:18,848
All of them love you a lot, Parvati.

869
01:03:18,900 --> 01:03:20,229
Mom.
- Mom.

870
01:03:26,943 --> 01:03:29,838
Kamla, how are you? Where is mom?

871
01:03:33,478 --> 01:03:37,451
Suresh. Suresh. It's you.
- Mom.

872
01:03:39,197 --> 01:03:42,434
Is Parvati alright?
- Yes, mom. She is absolutely fine.

873
01:03:42,612 --> 01:03:45,926
The kids, her mother-in-law,
all of them love her a lot.

874
01:03:47,382 --> 01:03:50,117
I want to meet Parvati.

875
01:03:50,620 --> 01:03:52,057
Please get her here once.

876
01:03:54,463 --> 01:03:58,160
Yes, mom. I will get her.
She also wants to come.

877
01:03:58,625 --> 01:04:00,943
But Manoharlal's nature
is a bit strange.

878
01:04:01,444 --> 01:04:04,589
He might not like it
if she comes here.

879
01:04:04,702 --> 01:04:06,175
Then let it be, son.

880
01:04:06,526 --> 01:04:09,410
We are happy that
she is happy there.

881
01:04:10,544 --> 01:04:12,999
What about her Asha and Ratanlal?

882
01:04:13,211 --> 01:04:16,304
Asha is good. But I don't
know anything about Ratanlal.

883
01:04:16,455 --> 01:04:19,426
He never comes home and I
haven't seen him either.

884
01:04:19,561 --> 01:04:20,916
Kamla, where are others?

885
01:04:23,003 --> 01:04:25,520
Have they gone to school?
Alright, mom. I'll leave.

886
01:04:25,728 --> 01:04:27,730
I am getting late for college.
- Yes, son.

887
01:04:27,906 --> 01:04:30,223
Go carefully.
- Yes, mom.

888
01:04:34,804 --> 01:04:39,497
I will apply first.
- No, I will.

889
01:04:39,753 --> 01:04:42,460
Enough. Don't fight.
Everyone will take a good bath.

890
01:04:56,661 --> 01:04:59,390
Asha, you continue.
I'll be right back.

891
01:05:02,796 --> 01:05:03,961
Did you call me?

892
01:05:04,924 --> 01:05:06,975
What are you doing?
- Oh c'mon!

893
01:05:07,283 --> 01:05:10,268
Leave me. Didn't you see the
kids are shouting there?

894
01:05:10,409 --> 01:05:12,454
Soap has entered
their eyes and ears.

895
01:05:12,475 --> 01:05:15,674
Let them shout. How are we bothered?
- What is wrong with you?

896
01:05:15,762 --> 01:05:18,350
Your younger sister is
standing there and you...

897
01:05:25,983 --> 01:05:28,909
I won't be able to come tomorrow.
Don't wait for me.

898
01:05:29,378 --> 01:05:32,570
Asha!
- Ratan!

899
01:05:35,491 --> 01:05:38,458
Take a look. I sold that cab and
I have taken a new private cab.

900
01:05:38,548 --> 01:05:41,332
I just have to give Rs 200 every month.
- That's okay, Ratan.

901
01:05:41,451 --> 01:05:42,837
But why don't you come home?

902
01:05:43,246 --> 01:05:46,846
You are having a fight with Manohar.
What have we done?

903
01:05:47,019 --> 01:05:49,813
At least come once in
a week to meet us.

904
01:05:49,893 --> 01:05:52,009
Why should I? First, I saw
Manohar do atrocities.

905
01:05:52,170 --> 01:05:54,997
Now you want me to come and see
our sister-in-law do atrocities.

906
01:05:55,047 --> 01:05:57,252
Atrocities! Who told you so?

907
01:05:57,434 --> 01:05:58,712
What's there to say?

908
01:05:59,001 --> 01:06:00,975
She is step-mom.
She is bound to do so.

909
01:06:01,074 --> 01:06:03,314
You are saying things
without knowing the truth.

910
01:06:03,600 --> 01:06:06,384
Come home and see. I swear, Ratan.

911
01:06:06,461 --> 01:06:10,034
We have got such a good sister-in-law
that no one can imagine.

912
01:06:10,226 --> 01:06:11,793
Really, Asha?
- Yes, Ratan.

913
01:06:11,921 --> 01:06:14,607
Oh! That means I don't
have to worry anymore.

914
01:06:15,673 --> 01:06:20,156
The bell is ringing. You should go.
I will come in meet soon. - Okay.

915
01:06:25,323 --> 01:06:28,048
Parvati, there is a prayer
session in the temple.

916
01:06:28,200 --> 01:06:29,720
Mom is asking me to
go along with her.

917
01:06:29,934 --> 01:06:31,195
Can I go?
- Of course.

918
01:06:31,647 --> 01:06:34,601
Should I take the car? - But the car
is out since morning, Asha.

919
01:06:34,738 --> 01:06:37,461
Alright, no problem. It's nearby.
We'll go walking.

920
01:06:37,583 --> 01:06:39,530
Come back soon.
- Sure, Parvati.

921
01:06:42,490 --> 01:06:49,681
"From the town of sleep, the angels.."

922
01:06:50,181 --> 01:06:55,097
"..have got a bag full of dreams."

923
01:06:56,967 --> 01:07:02,375
"The stars are also feeling sleepy.."

924
01:07:02,979 --> 01:07:09,084
"..when the moon came up the sky."

925
01:07:14,379 --> 01:07:20,523
"As the night has come up.."

926
01:07:21,205 --> 01:07:27,450
"..the entire world is sleeping."

927
01:07:27,964 --> 01:07:34,416
"You too, my dearest daughter.."

928
01:07:34,807 --> 01:07:41,567
"..close your eyes and enter
the land of dreams."

929
01:07:41,796 --> 01:07:44,498
I am asking you to come.

930
01:07:46,256 --> 01:07:48,542
Oh c'mon! Just come.

931
01:07:48,601 --> 01:07:52,412
"How do I come.."

932
01:07:52,765 --> 01:07:57,533
"..unless my dearest daughter.."

933
01:07:58,082 --> 01:08:02,869
"..falls fast asleep."

934
01:08:03,659 --> 01:08:09,981
"Keep patience and don't be wild."

935
01:08:10,310 --> 01:08:16,889
"What is this impatience all about?"

936
01:08:39,038 --> 01:08:40,424
Oh!

937
01:08:43,057 --> 01:08:47,312
What's the hurry? Didn't I tell you,
I am coming after making Munni sleep.

938
01:08:47,353 --> 01:08:50,548
Munni will keep crying all night.
I will go crazy by then.

939
01:08:50,870 --> 01:08:52,889
What?
- What are you doing?

940
01:08:52,980 --> 01:08:55,001
Alright. Go out. Get out.
- No.

941
01:09:03,758 --> 01:09:04,899
Why are you turning the lights off?

942
01:09:05,448 --> 01:09:07,988
Is this important?
- Yes, I am scared.

943
01:09:08,087 --> 01:09:09,503
No.
- Go out! Go!

944
01:09:09,549 --> 01:09:10,962
Alright. Let it be.

945
01:09:28,779 --> 01:09:31,725
Look, Munni is crying.

946
01:09:34,530 --> 01:09:37,056
I think she is coming
upstairs looking for me.

947
01:09:43,601 --> 01:09:45,520
Leave me! Leave me!
- No.

948
01:09:45,587 --> 01:09:48,110
Leave me! Munni might
fall of the stairs. - No!

949
01:09:48,157 --> 01:09:51,275
Let her fall off!
- How can you do that?

950
01:09:53,421 --> 01:09:56,559
Munni! My daughter! Oh dear!

951
01:09:56,875 --> 01:09:58,698
Oh Munni! My dear!

952
01:09:58,756 --> 01:10:00,201
Were you looking for me?

953
01:10:05,718 --> 01:10:09,321
What can we do? Her fate is such!

954
01:10:09,748 --> 01:10:13,388
Oh God! Such a good wife..

955
01:10:13,511 --> 01:10:15,330
..for such a bad man!

956
01:10:26,724 --> 01:10:29,821
Hand over Munni to Asha and come
with me. Did you hear me?

957
01:10:44,440 --> 01:10:45,919
Who is the cab driver here?

958
01:10:47,933 --> 01:10:49,641
Driver!
- Yes?

959
01:10:49,704 --> 01:10:51,106
I need to go to Hotel Grand.
Will you?

960
01:10:52,273 --> 01:10:55,397
C'mon, sit. Hurry up.

961
01:10:57,434 --> 01:10:58,685
Let's go.

962
01:11:09,437 --> 01:11:12,118
C'mon, get off.
- Where have you got me?

963
01:11:12,195 --> 01:11:16,557
Hotel. - What is this? Why would we
leave the house in stay in a hotel?

964
01:11:16,616 --> 01:11:19,283
The kids have irritated
in the house.

965
01:11:19,452 --> 01:11:22,173
Are we able to sit in peace
at home for a while?

966
01:11:22,324 --> 01:11:24,454
Someone asks for food,
someone for milk.

967
01:11:24,536 --> 01:11:25,702
I don't like all this.

968
01:11:25,741 --> 01:11:27,388
Get off.
- What are you saying?

969
01:11:27,919 --> 01:11:32,695
Around those kids, we are able to
see each other, that's enough.

970
01:11:32,994 --> 01:11:36,435
In between their shouts, we are
able to talk to each other.

971
01:11:36,776 --> 01:11:38,115
That's what family is about.

972
01:11:38,198 --> 01:11:39,850
Are you trying to teach
me about family?

973
01:11:39,999 --> 01:11:42,931
Get off right now.
- No. I am scared.

974
01:11:43,013 --> 01:11:45,833
Why are you scared?
Your husband is with you.

975
01:11:45,958 --> 01:11:47,167
That's why I am scared.

976
01:11:47,345 --> 01:11:50,444
When people see us here, will
they think you are my husband?

977
01:11:50,948 --> 01:11:52,448
Why are you talking about others?

978
01:11:53,040 --> 01:11:54,825
I myself considered
you wrong, Parvati.

979
01:11:55,092 --> 01:11:57,976
You know me?
- Yes, Parvati. I am Ratan.

980
01:11:58,730 --> 01:12:02,018
But I am unfortunate to have not
been able to meet you till date.

981
01:12:02,823 --> 01:12:06,889
I am sure you know by now that
my brother is strange man.

982
01:12:07,310 --> 01:12:09,909
He has a great wife like
you yet he hasn't changed.

983
01:12:09,972 --> 01:12:11,441
Hey, shut up!

984
01:12:11,513 --> 01:12:14,126
Don't shout. You are elder
to me that's why I am quiet.

985
01:12:14,209 --> 01:12:18,119
Else, I would've thrown you out
of the cab within no time.

986
01:12:18,542 --> 01:12:19,509
Let's go.
- No, Parvati.

987
01:12:19,591 --> 01:12:23,269
Let's go. - Manohar, if you force her
I will shout and call out to people.

988
01:12:23,359 --> 01:12:24,593
Stay there, Parvati.

989
01:12:35,830 --> 01:12:39,564
Come, Parvati. Go inside.

990
01:12:41,451 --> 01:12:44,976
Manohar, we are lucky to have her.

991
01:12:45,228 --> 01:12:46,591
Make sure she isn't sad.

992
01:12:46,672 --> 01:12:49,881
Go. Go!
- I am going. But I will keep coming.

993
01:12:50,241 --> 01:12:52,620
You will keep coming!
This is such a pain!

994
01:12:52,702 --> 01:12:55,119
Kids irritate me at home
and my brother outside.

995
01:12:56,296 --> 01:12:58,820
Parvati.
- Yes?

996
01:12:58,842 --> 01:13:00,562
Tomorrow morning we will
go to Mussorie - Mussorie?

997
01:13:00,585 --> 01:13:01,700
Yes, be ready.

998
01:13:01,772 --> 01:13:03,338
But...
- I said, be ready

999
01:13:03,616 --> 01:13:04,642
Okay.

1000
01:13:09,890 --> 01:13:13,640
Now will you come?
- I am coming, one minute.

1001
01:13:13,953 --> 01:13:15,545
If you don't come by
one minute then...

1002
01:13:15,771 --> 01:13:20,584
The almighty has granted such a beautiful
face, why do you need make-up?

1003
01:13:20,647 --> 01:13:22,899
We have reach Mussorie by night.
But she isn't leaving.

1004
01:13:22,990 --> 01:13:26,656
C'mon! Let's go.
- Yes! Yeah! We are going.

1005
01:13:26,708 --> 01:13:29,110
All of us are going!
- Yes, all us are going.

1006
01:13:29,185 --> 01:13:30,858
Go and sit in the car.

1007
01:13:33,346 --> 01:13:34,372
Hey.

1008
01:13:35,958 --> 01:13:37,105
Come here.

1009
01:13:37,622 --> 01:13:38,977
What did I tell you?

1010
01:13:39,534 --> 01:13:41,361
You said, we'll be
going to Mussorie.

1011
01:13:41,429 --> 01:13:43,731
What does that mean?
- What does it mean?

1012
01:13:43,828 --> 01:13:46,833
I meant, we will be able to
leave peacefully for some days.

1013
01:13:46,855 --> 01:13:48,678
So, I had said only the
two of us will be going.

1014
01:13:48,700 --> 01:13:51,144
When did I say that the
kids will come along?

1015
01:13:51,197 --> 01:13:52,680
Just the two of us?
- Yes.

1016
01:13:53,403 --> 01:13:56,310
What is so funny?
- Nothing.

1017
01:13:56,490 --> 01:13:59,322
But what so interesting in
Mussorie and Shimla at this age?

1018
01:13:59,705 --> 01:14:01,247
Are you coming alone or not?

1019
01:14:01,553 --> 01:14:05,000
Listen, it's my mistake that
I asked them to come along.

1020
01:14:05,214 --> 01:14:08,088
But now I have told them,
let them come along.

1021
01:14:08,167 --> 01:14:11,555
Hey!
- Listen, if we leave them alone now..

1022
01:14:11,614 --> 01:14:13,280
..then they will be really sad.

1023
01:14:13,410 --> 01:14:14,749
Is that so?

1024
01:14:14,771 --> 01:14:18,456
Alright. Then no one will go.
Now no one will go to Mussorie.

1025
01:14:18,603 --> 01:14:22,800
I am married to you and
hence I can't do anywhere.

1026
01:14:22,865 --> 01:14:24,845
But I will surely go
the cremation ground.- Listen.

1027
01:14:24,865 --> 01:14:26,007
I don't want to.

1028
01:14:32,850 --> 01:14:34,486
Parvati, please come here.

1029
01:14:34,538 --> 01:14:36,710
What is it, Asha?
- Please come.

1030
01:14:39,844 --> 01:14:43,346
Parvati, listen to me.
Go with him alone.

1031
01:14:43,424 --> 01:14:46,024
What? What are you saying?

1032
01:14:46,136 --> 01:14:48,079
I have a reason to say so.

1033
01:14:49,309 --> 01:14:51,617
Mom, let's go.
- Let's go!

1034
01:14:51,700 --> 01:14:53,393
Wait! I am coming.

1035
01:14:53,934 --> 01:14:56,907
Look at them.
How can I go without them?

1036
01:14:57,005 --> 01:14:59,604
Parvati, don't get me wrong.

1037
01:14:59,906 --> 01:15:02,994
You have come home just now.
Before you came..

1038
01:15:03,092 --> 01:15:05,140
..I took care of them.

1039
01:15:05,904 --> 01:15:08,258
You don't know how Manohar is.

1040
01:15:08,339 --> 01:15:10,836
How will I know?
- I'll tell you.

1041
01:15:11,820 --> 01:15:14,984
A sister shouldn't say all
this about her own brother.

1042
01:15:15,078 --> 01:15:17,125
But I have to say this
because of these kids.

1043
01:15:17,865 --> 01:15:19,713
He is very stubborn, Parvati.

1044
01:15:20,081 --> 01:15:24,056
Because of his attitude,
my first sister-in-law died.

1045
01:15:24,891 --> 01:15:26,558
A kid every year.

1046
01:15:27,390 --> 01:15:31,013
If my brother doesn't get what
he wants at that very moment..

1047
01:15:31,035 --> 01:15:33,344
..then he creates a ruckus.

1048
01:15:33,496 --> 01:15:35,730
He will start breaking things.

1049
01:15:36,134 --> 01:15:38,905
He picks up things and
throws them on the kids.

1050
01:15:39,629 --> 01:15:44,594
Do you want him to hit the kids?
- No. I didn't know all this.

1051
01:15:44,658 --> 01:15:47,840
I will go right now. But, Asha..

1052
01:15:48,272 --> 01:15:49,825
..take care of the kids.

1053
01:15:50,204 --> 01:15:53,636
If there's a problem then
call them that very moment. - Okay.

1054
01:15:54,795 --> 01:15:57,107
Parvati, go from this side.

1055
01:15:57,234 --> 01:15:59,688
Let me make an excuse and
take the kids upstairs.

1056
01:15:59,998 --> 01:16:01,461
Go with Manohar.

1057
01:16:16,115 --> 01:16:18,459
Listen, I have handled
the situation.

1058
01:16:18,889 --> 01:16:22,325
We'll take the kids some other time.
Today, we'll go together.

1059
01:16:22,754 --> 01:16:25,787
Had you said this before,
I would've been happier.

1060
01:16:25,920 --> 01:16:29,147
It's not too late.
Here, wear your coat.

1061
01:16:30,756 --> 01:16:35,459
I asked you to come to Mussorie
with me, there's a reason.

1062
01:16:35,499 --> 01:16:37,636
Unless you come along how
will you understand.

1063
01:16:37,841 --> 01:16:41,696
Now I am coming. I will understand.
- Let's go.

1064
01:16:54,998 --> 01:16:56,512
Yes, Manoharlal speaking.

1065
01:16:56,704 --> 01:16:58,843
Hello, Mr. Malhotra here.

1066
01:16:58,914 --> 01:17:00,921
Hello, Mr. Malhotra. How are you?

1067
01:17:00,968 --> 01:17:03,836
Everyone is waiting
for you at the party.

1068
01:17:03,886 --> 01:17:05,099
You haven't come here yet!

1069
01:17:05,239 --> 01:17:07,491
Good very good.
I am leaving in 5 minutes.

1070
01:17:07,576 --> 01:17:09,026
C'mon! Hurry up!

1071
01:17:09,791 --> 01:17:12,122
Parvati, hurry up. Quick.

1072
01:17:14,374 --> 01:17:16,843
Let's go.
- How long...

1073
01:17:21,691 --> 01:17:24,428
Hey! What is this you are wearing?

1074
01:17:24,594 --> 01:17:26,552
Are you feeling cold?

1075
01:17:26,617 --> 01:17:29,850
You have covered your
whole body, idiot!

1076
01:17:29,945 --> 01:17:31,902
Do you know the kind of
place we are going to?

1077
01:17:31,990 --> 01:17:33,876
It is not any ordinary
man who has invited me.

1078
01:17:33,900 --> 01:17:37,039
He has a science degree from
England's Oxford University.

1079
01:17:37,140 --> 01:17:38,974
He has traveled all over the world.

1080
01:17:39,049 --> 01:17:41,367
England, France, America.

1081
01:17:41,443 --> 01:17:44,444
He called me as a
gentleman with my wife.

1082
01:17:44,590 --> 01:17:49,004
How can you come with these clothes?
You illiterate, woman!

1083
01:17:49,067 --> 01:17:51,229
Go and cut grasses in some field.

1084
01:17:51,355 --> 01:17:55,242
What can I do? I don't know how to
dress up the way you want me to.

1085
01:17:55,457 --> 01:17:58,577
I know you don't know that.
How will you know?

1086
01:17:58,747 --> 01:18:00,503
You are always inside the house.

1087
01:18:00,584 --> 01:18:04,445
You are always with the kids or
in the kitchen. How will you know..

1088
01:18:04,500 --> 01:18:06,564
..about modern fashion like this?

1089
01:18:06,671 --> 01:18:10,225
That's why I used to ask you to come
and watch English films with me.

1090
01:18:10,344 --> 01:18:12,493
They are such amazing movies.

1091
01:18:12,684 --> 01:18:16,175
'Woman By Night', 'Paris By Night',
'World By Night."

1092
01:18:16,216 --> 01:18:18,482
The story is just like
the name of the film.

1093
01:18:18,591 --> 01:18:22,903
Had you seen one movie, you would've
transformed by now. Shameless

1094
01:18:23,580 --> 01:18:25,366
Why did you wear a sari?

1095
01:18:25,630 --> 01:18:27,702
Why didn't you wear the
dress I bought for you?

1096
01:18:28,026 --> 01:18:29,801
What is this? Is this the
way to do your hair?

1097
01:18:30,003 --> 01:18:32,051
I had asked you to dress
your hair properly.

1098
01:18:32,087 --> 01:18:34,494
You applied oil in your
hair and combed it.

1099
01:18:34,689 --> 01:18:37,884
Modern hair dressing
should be like a bee-hive.

1100
01:18:37,967 --> 01:18:40,300
It should be like a Saint Narayana.

1101
01:18:40,409 --> 01:18:44,290
Why didn't you do that? Why didn't
you apply nail polish to the nails?

1102
01:18:44,375 --> 01:18:46,743
You won't change.
I will dress hence forth.

1103
01:18:46,782 --> 01:18:50,732
Let it be.
- No way. People will laugh. Let's go.

1104
01:18:53,427 --> 01:18:55,191
Just a minute.

1105
01:18:56,271 --> 01:18:58,944
Don't move. Don't move. That's it.

1106
01:19:01,891 --> 01:19:04,736
Get up. C'mon. Look at you.

1107
01:19:04,804 --> 01:19:07,585
You look like a woman from Paris.

1108
01:19:07,673 --> 01:19:11,279
Oh God! What is this nonsense?
What have I done? This looks horrible.

1109
01:19:11,316 --> 01:19:14,161
Is it bad? You will have to come
like this.- No. I won't.

1110
01:19:14,220 --> 01:19:16,450
Why not?
- Let me wear something over it.

1111
01:19:16,501 --> 01:19:18,502
No, no. You won't wear
anything over it.

1112
01:19:18,657 --> 01:19:20,173
Then I won't come.

1113
01:19:20,239 --> 01:19:22,289
Oh God! This is such a pain!

1114
01:19:23,094 --> 01:19:25,391
You are messing with the
beauty of this dress. Take it.

1115
01:19:25,559 --> 01:19:27,314
What is this? Is this a cloth?

1116
01:19:27,425 --> 01:19:29,147
Why not?
- This is like a net.

1117
01:19:29,259 --> 01:19:30,526
Give me something else.

1118
01:19:31,077 --> 01:19:34,882
You will have to wear this. Women these
days wear these kind of clothes.

1119
01:19:34,905 --> 01:19:36,223
Let's go. And listen.

1120
01:19:36,423 --> 01:19:38,067
Do you know what you
have to go there and do?

1121
01:19:38,182 --> 01:19:39,645
What?
- We will go there.

1122
01:19:40,021 --> 01:19:41,942
Rich people will be around.
- So what?

1123
01:19:42,110 --> 01:19:44,440
People from high
societies will be there.

1124
01:19:44,488 --> 01:19:48,655
As you reach there shake hands
with them and greet them. - What?

1125
01:19:48,879 --> 01:19:50,966
I have to shake hands
with unknown men. No way!

1126
01:19:51,065 --> 01:19:53,307
Dear Lord! You are such an illiterate!

1127
01:19:53,360 --> 01:19:56,047
If you don't do that
they will laugh at me.

1128
01:19:56,141 --> 01:19:59,291
As soon as we reach
there, forget about me.

1129
01:19:59,440 --> 01:20:00,835
Don't look at me.

1130
01:20:01,342 --> 01:20:04,388
Just greet them and shake hands.
Show it to me.

1131
01:20:05,072 --> 01:20:08,493
Hello!
- What is this? Are you crying?

1132
01:20:08,671 --> 01:20:10,261
Just say. 'Hello.'
- Hello.

1133
01:20:10,413 --> 01:20:11,933
Now let's go.

1134
01:20:13,248 --> 01:20:14,465
Be careful.

1135
01:20:14,489 --> 01:20:16,738
Nonsense! Get up.

1136
01:20:18,974 --> 01:20:21,319
What sort of shoes are these?
Such big heels.

1137
01:20:21,448 --> 01:20:22,754
Can I hold them in
my hands and walk?

1138
01:20:22,864 --> 01:20:28,119
Why don't you place it on your head?
Walk for a while, you'll get used to it.

1139
01:20:28,190 --> 01:20:31,464
Great. C'mon. Good.

1140
01:20:33,342 --> 01:20:34,697
Come, Manoharlal, come.

1141
01:20:35,005 --> 01:20:36,967
You are so late.
- I am sorry.

1142
01:20:37,003 --> 01:20:42,209
That's alright. So you have got your
daughter along. - No. She is my wife.

1143
01:20:42,283 --> 01:20:43,680
Second wife.
- Really?

1144
01:20:43,695 --> 01:20:46,431
Nice meeting you.
- Shake hands with him.

1145
01:20:46,513 --> 01:20:48,227
Hello.
- Waiter!

1146
01:20:49,759 --> 01:20:51,873
Take it.
- Thank you.

1147
01:20:52,127 --> 01:20:53,736
Please take your seat.
- Thank you.

1148
01:20:56,510 --> 01:20:58,604
Sit. Sit down.

1149
01:21:00,543 --> 01:21:02,079
Hey, what are you doing?

1150
01:21:04,399 --> 01:21:08,258
Mr. James, sorry for the delay.
- Oh! Don't worry.

1151
01:21:08,466 --> 01:21:10,560
Ladies and gentlemen,
take your partners.

1152
01:21:42,206 --> 01:21:43,987
Come, let's dance.

1153
01:21:44,309 --> 01:21:46,441
Oh God! What is this?
- Why?

1154
01:21:46,623 --> 01:21:48,760
I don't know all this.
- What don't you know?

1155
01:21:48,827 --> 01:21:52,724
Just bend a bit and get up.
It's so easy. Everyone is doing it.

1156
01:21:52,834 --> 01:21:56,991
I don't know how to dance.
- I will kill you. Just dance.

1157
01:21:57,013 --> 01:21:58,296
I beg of you.

1158
01:21:58,318 --> 01:22:01,501
No need. Just shake your legs.
C'mon.

1159
01:23:52,191 --> 01:23:58,843
"I am in love with you.."

1160
01:23:59,449 --> 01:24:05,855
"..but I won't be able to tell you."

1161
01:24:05,897 --> 01:24:15,996
"I am in love with you but I
will not be able to tell you."

1162
01:24:16,029 --> 01:24:20,673
"There is a smile on my lips.."

1163
01:24:20,738 --> 01:24:25,844
"..but I won't be able to tell you."

1164
01:24:25,895 --> 01:24:31,380
"I am in love with you but I
will not be able to tell you."

1165
01:24:53,236 --> 01:25:03,331
"Sometimes I am happy, I have desires,
my heart beats pace and I am confused."

1166
01:25:03,400 --> 01:25:13,513
"My heart is in a strange condition
but I am unable to say it."

1167
01:25:13,573 --> 01:25:18,709
"I am in love with you."

1168
01:25:33,581 --> 01:25:43,822
"You are waiting to hear about
the condition of my heart."

1169
01:25:48,552 --> 01:25:58,488
"You are waiting to hear about
the condition of my heart."

1170
01:25:58,601 --> 01:26:08,507
"I have the time to tell you
everything but I unable to say it."

1171
01:26:08,633 --> 01:26:14,336
"I am in love with you."

1172
01:26:38,079 --> 01:26:39,918
Mom.

1173
01:26:40,743 --> 01:26:41,960
What is it?

1174
01:26:42,085 --> 01:26:43,848
Well... Well...

1175
01:26:44,062 --> 01:26:46,196
Well... What?

1176
01:26:46,390 --> 01:26:50,633
Suresh has gone and sat at the
dining area. Shouldn't you serve him?

1177
01:26:51,048 --> 01:26:55,096
Why you asking me? Go and serve him.

1178
01:26:55,132 --> 01:26:57,394
No, I am really scared.

1179
01:26:57,450 --> 01:27:00,230
You are scared!
You are scared of that boy!

1180
01:27:00,438 --> 01:27:04,182
He quietly comes and leave quietly.

