..would you be able to look at Asha?

1413
01:47:13,744 --> 01:47:17,667
What's the point of crying now?
He has asked you to leave.

1414
01:47:18,146 --> 01:47:21,540
I cannot keep you here
against his wishes.

1415
01:47:21,736 --> 01:47:23,039
Go away.

1416
01:47:26,228 --> 01:47:27,484
Listen.

1417
01:47:30,243 --> 01:47:35,125
If you have a bit of shame
then fulfill your promise.

1418
01:47:35,349 --> 01:47:38,190
Go and arrange for the money yourself.

1419
01:47:38,420 --> 01:47:41,449
Somehow, complete your
studies and become a doctor.

1420
01:47:42,140 --> 01:47:45,686
Until then if she
remains single for you..

1421
01:47:46,013 --> 01:47:48,969
..then come back as a
doctor in this house..

1422
01:47:49,399 --> 01:47:52,740
..and ask her from him officially.

1423
01:47:53,288 --> 01:47:57,204
Even then if he doesn't agree,
I will take care of everything else.

1424
01:47:57,431 --> 01:47:58,952
Now go away.

1425
01:48:43,866 --> 01:48:53,770
"A woman's life is like a swing,
at this end and at that end."

1426
01:48:53,836 --> 01:49:03,322
"A woman's life is like a swing,
at this end and at that end."

1427
01:49:03,372 --> 01:49:12,713
"Sometimes there's smile on her face,
sometimes tears rolling down her eyes."

1428
01:49:12,907 --> 01:49:23,604
"A woman's life is like a swing,
at this end and at that end."

1429
01:49:29,087 --> 01:49:33,496
Suresh! Come, son.
Didn't you go to college today?

1430
01:49:33,797 --> 01:49:37,530
No, mom. I thought of
meeting all of you.

1431
01:49:37,601 --> 01:49:40,116
Kamla, look Suresh has come.

1432
01:49:41,865 --> 01:49:44,642
Son, wait I'll get some tea for you.

1433
01:50:04,093 --> 01:50:05,692
Take it, son.

1434
01:50:07,853 --> 01:50:11,093
Suresh, may God always
bless Manoharlal.

1435
01:50:11,651 --> 01:50:15,562
He sends money every month,
we manage with it.

1436
01:50:16,532 --> 01:50:19,822
Please ask him to send this
month's money today itself.

1437
01:50:20,654 --> 01:50:23,205
Why, mom?
- There are no grains in the house.

1438
01:50:24,184 --> 01:50:25,967
How do I hide anything from you?

1439
01:50:26,091 --> 01:50:29,934
Your sisters haven't eaten
anything since yesterday.

1440
01:50:34,882 --> 01:50:35,937
What happened, son?

1441
01:50:36,939 --> 01:50:38,064
Nothing, mom.

1442
01:51:17,738 --> 01:51:19,364
There's no one to help me push it.

1443
01:51:19,767 --> 01:51:23,365
I think the government has solved
the problem of unemployment.

1444
01:51:23,816 --> 01:51:26,528
Alright. I think I
will have to push it.

1445
01:51:29,462 --> 01:51:31,431
What are you doing?
- Pushing the car.

1446
01:51:31,498 --> 01:51:33,298
Really? I hope you aren't
trying to steal anything.

1447
01:51:33,397 --> 01:51:35,945
No. I am pushing the car.
- I see that.

1448
01:51:36,196 --> 01:51:38,873
Thank you very much.
The petrol is over.

1449
01:51:38,941 --> 01:51:41,139
We'll have to take it
till the petrol pump.

1450
01:51:41,262 --> 01:51:42,851
You seem to be decent man.

1451
01:51:44,690 --> 01:51:46,268
Alright. Stop.

1452
01:51:48,445 --> 01:51:50,887
Hey, put 10 liter of petrol.

1453
01:51:51,575 --> 01:51:52,658
Come here.

1454
01:51:54,789 --> 01:51:56,178
Take this.
- What's this?

1455
01:51:56,228 --> 01:52:00,387
No one would pay anything for
pushing the car. I paid Rs 2 to you.

1456
01:52:00,650 --> 01:52:03,573
Do you know why? Because
you helped me voluntarily.

1457
01:52:03,627 --> 01:52:06,137
And you want more money.
- That's not what I meant.

1458
01:52:06,523 --> 01:52:09,309
I am desperately roaming around
to earn this Rs 2 since morning.

1459
01:52:09,625 --> 01:52:12,694
But I didn't know that I will
be able to earn it so soon.

1460
01:52:13,010 --> 01:52:14,458
My family is dying of hunger.

1461
01:52:14,486 --> 01:52:16,627
If you roam about in these
clothes all around the city

1462
01:52:16,680 --> 01:52:18,397
then the family is bound
to die of hunger.

1463
01:52:18,480 --> 01:52:22,532
That's not true. We had
trusted on a rich man's word.

1464
01:52:22,792 --> 01:52:24,239
That's why we are suffering.

1465
01:52:24,428 --> 01:52:25,512
Listen.

1466
01:52:25,580 --> 01:52:26,923
If you don't mind,
can I say something?

1467
01:52:26,977 --> 01:52:29,223
If you say something good then
why would I mind. Say it.

1468
01:52:29,716 --> 01:52:32,318
Please help me get a job.
- Job? Me?

1469
01:52:32,534 --> 01:52:34,096
How can I get you a job?

1470
01:52:34,402 --> 01:52:36,495
You seem to be an educated person.

1471
01:52:36,788 --> 01:52:40,760
Until I get a good job,
keep me as a cleaner.

1472
01:52:40,812 --> 01:52:42,034
Cleaner?

1473
01:52:47,996 --> 01:52:49,430
Will you be able to do it?
- Absolutely!

1474
01:52:49,925 --> 01:52:52,558
Alright. You will get Rs 3 everyday.
Agreed? - Agreed.

1475
01:52:52,773 --> 01:52:54,518
Come tomorrow.
- Listen.

1476
01:52:54,618 --> 01:52:56,845
Now what?
- Where's your garage?

1477
01:52:56,905 --> 01:53:00,572
You are strange. Even if you
ask an animal in the city..

1478
01:53:00,655 --> 01:53:03,855
..where the garage of a rich man's
brother, Ratanlal cab driver..

1479
01:53:03,907 --> 01:53:06,000
..they will tell you. Go on.

1480
01:53:06,614 --> 01:53:11,234
Kamla, Vimla, Shanta...
I have got food. - Suresh! Suresh!

1481
01:53:11,291 --> 01:53:12,869
Kamla, take this. Feed them.

1482
01:53:12,920 --> 01:53:16,312
Kamla. Kamla.
- You too have some.

1483
01:53:16,394 --> 01:53:18,623
Go slow. Don't shout.

1484
01:53:18,765 --> 01:53:21,157
What is the matter?
- Mom, I have got a job.

1485
01:53:21,240 --> 01:53:24,382
Job? What job?
- I will tell that later.

1486
01:53:24,506 --> 01:53:26,625
First, take this money, go and
get some rice and lentils.

1487
01:53:27,387 --> 01:53:29,699
I have had, Kamla. Give it to mom.

1488
01:53:29,885 --> 01:53:31,007
Keep it there, dear.

1489
01:53:31,682 --> 01:53:35,125
Mom, I am telling something.
Always remember it.

1490
01:53:35,621 --> 01:53:37,907
A man is the one who eats whatever
he gets out of hard work.

1491
01:53:38,281 --> 01:53:41,243
The one who wants to live
on someone else's money..

1492
01:53:41,495 --> 01:53:44,436
..suffers just like our
family is suffering.

1493
01:53:44,657 --> 01:53:47,038
This is my experience, mom.
I am telling the truth.

1494
01:53:48,391 --> 01:53:51,715
Take it.
- Right. You used to sit ideal here.

1495
01:53:51,761 --> 01:53:54,318
Now you are earning because
of us, so you are being rude.

1496
01:53:54,417 --> 01:53:57,340
Enough, man. How much will
you clean? Go and rest.

1497
01:53:57,360 --> 01:54:00,730
I don't need to take rest.
- At least my cab needs to rest.

1498
01:54:00,811 --> 01:54:03,613
You are cleaning as if
your washing vessels.

1499
01:54:03,695 --> 01:54:08,211
Elderly people have said, one should
work a bit and rest a bit as well.

1500
01:54:12,856 --> 01:54:15,423
When you start, you
don't seem to stop.

1501
01:54:28,217 --> 01:54:30,450
Hello, who are you?

1502
01:54:30,560 --> 01:54:31,788
I am Suresh here.

1503
01:54:31,922 --> 01:54:34,920
Uncle Suresh. I am Vinod.

1504
01:54:35,025 --> 01:54:37,269
Vinod, is dad home?

1505
01:54:37,368 --> 01:54:40,132
Yes, he is.
- Will you help me with something?

1506
01:54:40,291 --> 01:54:41,743
Sure. Tell me.

1507
01:54:42,043 --> 01:54:44,629
Make sure your dad
doesn't know about it.

1508
01:54:44,882 --> 01:54:47,621
Quietly go and get Asha on the line.

1509
01:54:47,927 --> 01:54:52,595
Uncle, if aunt comes here
dad will learn about it.

1510
01:54:52,729 --> 01:54:55,197
She is inside the room studying.

1511
01:54:55,413 --> 01:54:57,360
I'll take the telephone to her room.

1512
01:54:57,383 --> 01:55:00,960
Okay. You are very smart.
Go and give it.

1513
01:55:11,120 --> 01:55:14,218
Hey, why are you getting
the telephone here?

1514
01:55:15,778 --> 01:55:18,460
Uncle Suresh, wants to talk to you.

1515
01:55:22,783 --> 01:55:24,835
Hello, Asha here.

1516
01:55:24,962 --> 01:55:27,753
Suresh here. How are you, Asha?

1517
01:55:29,222 --> 01:55:31,315
Asha, why are you crying?

1518
01:55:33,461 --> 01:55:34,689
Tell me.

1519
01:55:35,226 --> 01:55:38,111
Suresh, I hope you won't forget me.

1520
01:55:38,229 --> 01:55:39,634
What are you saying, Asha?

1521
01:55:40,103 --> 01:55:43,205
If you were away from me then
I would've forgotten you.

1522
01:55:43,632 --> 01:55:45,334
But now we are one.

1523
01:55:45,533 --> 01:55:46,953
How can I forget you?

1524
01:55:52,239 --> 01:55:55,749
Is this guy speaking on
the phone or cleaning it?

1525
01:55:56,413 --> 01:55:59,959
Asha, how is Parvati?
- What can I say?

1526
01:56:00,460 --> 01:56:02,554
Parvati, keeps crying all day.

1527
01:56:03,449 --> 01:56:06,083
Complete your studies
anyhow, Suresh.

1528
01:56:06,135 --> 01:56:08,468
I came out from there with the
idea of completing my studies.

1529
01:56:08,731 --> 01:56:11,816
But Asha, my family members
are in a bad condition.

1530
01:56:12,001 --> 01:56:13,986
I can't even think about studying.

1531
01:56:14,038 --> 01:56:16,658
No. What are you saying?

1532
01:56:16,782 --> 01:56:20,506
Yes, Asha. Your brother, Manoharlal
is responsible for that.

1533
01:56:22,653 --> 01:56:24,414
Asha. Manoharlal.

1534
01:56:24,748 --> 01:56:26,139
My brother and sister.

1535
01:56:26,946 --> 01:56:27,873
Who is he?

1536
01:56:28,008 --> 01:56:31,593
They used to send money to our house,
now they have stopped it.

1537
01:56:32,470 --> 01:56:34,445
The condition of the
house is very bad Asha..

1538
01:56:34,935 --> 01:56:36,863
..but with effort I got a small job.

1539
01:56:37,706 --> 01:56:41,192
Whatever I earn,
I somehow manage to support my family.

1540
01:56:41,686 --> 01:56:44,676
But Asha I will try to
complete my studies.

1541
01:56:44,973 --> 01:56:48,326
Asha, I will call you
at this time every day.

1542
01:56:48,581 --> 01:56:51,507
And I will wait for your
call every day at this time.

1543
01:56:53,195 --> 01:56:54,938
Hello?
- Hello?

1544
01:56:55,018 --> 01:56:55,850
Who are you? Hello?

1545
01:56:55,974 --> 01:56:58,650
Idiot!
- I am Ratanlal. Not idiot!

1546
01:56:58,685 --> 01:57:01,487
Ratan! Was Asha speaking
to you all this while?

1547
01:57:01,652 --> 01:57:03,702
Yes, she was talking to me.
Who else?

1548
01:57:03,807 --> 01:57:07,090
Donkey! When you have left home,
why do you have to call?

1549
01:57:07,166 --> 01:57:11,588
Donkey's elder brother, if you can
talk properly to me then it's okay.

1550
01:57:11,726 --> 01:57:14,443
If you want me to talk like you..

1551
01:57:14,564 --> 01:57:16,056
..then I will talk to
you when I meet you.

1552
01:57:16,175 --> 01:57:17,465
I am cutting the call.

1553
01:57:21,833 --> 01:57:23,892
So, that's what you are doing.
Come out.

1554
01:57:24,344 --> 01:57:26,392
Look, don't get me wrong.

1555
01:57:26,471 --> 01:57:28,886
The girl I was talking
to is a relative.

1556
01:57:28,974 --> 01:57:30,364
Relative. What do you mean?

1557
01:57:30,417 --> 01:57:31,841
She is my brother-in-law's
younger sister.

1558
01:57:31,952 --> 01:57:33,454
Brother-in-law? What do you mean?

1559
01:57:33,556 --> 01:57:35,893
My sister's husband.
I was talking to his sister.

1560
01:57:36,045 --> 01:57:38,721
Since how many days is
this affair going on?

1561
01:57:38,803 --> 01:57:40,971
Well, I...
- Alright. Don't tell me.

1562
01:57:41,036 --> 01:57:45,833
Tell me one thing. If you face problems
and troubles, will you still be with her?

1563
01:57:45,933 --> 01:57:48,450
Even if I die...
- You will take her along.

1564
01:57:48,473 --> 01:57:49,780
I think so.

1565
01:57:49,911 --> 01:57:52,438
Does the girl feel the same way?
- Both of us feel the same way.

1566
01:57:52,522 --> 01:57:54,165
Now listen to what I have to say.

1567
01:57:54,321 --> 01:57:57,125
Stand here. Don't move.
Put your hands down.

1568
01:57:57,747 --> 01:57:58,868
Wait, I am coming.

1569
01:58:01,148 --> 01:58:04,371
Oh God! I think I will lose my job.

1570
01:58:28,757 --> 01:58:31,898
So, is she the relative you
were talking about. - Yes.

1571
01:58:32,072 --> 01:58:34,209
Is she your brother-in-law's sister?

1572
01:58:35,186 --> 01:58:37,848
Yes. Do you know who
your brother-in-law is?

1573
01:58:38,478 --> 01:58:40,185
Speak up.
- Who is he?

1574
01:58:40,297 --> 01:58:41,718
He is my elder brother.

1575
01:58:42,754 --> 01:58:45,374
Asha.
- Yes, Suresh. He is my brother.

1576
01:58:45,576 --> 01:58:49,079
That's great. You spoke
to her in front of me.

1577
01:58:49,141 --> 01:58:52,762
Ratan. - Quiet. Nowadays,
lovers speak over the phone..

1578
01:58:52,858 --> 01:58:54,261
..for such a long time.

1579
01:58:54,641 --> 01:58:57,812
I am telling the two of you.
If you want to talk to each other..

1580
01:58:57,937 --> 01:58:59,387
..let me know in the future. Got it?

1581
01:58:59,609 --> 01:59:01,046
Now go and talk.

1582
01:59:01,128 --> 01:59:03,706
Ratan, this is not the time to talk.

1583
01:59:03,969 --> 01:59:06,322
There are two very important things
that we need to finish right now.

1584
01:59:06,408 --> 01:59:08,981
Which ones?
- Didn't I tell you while coming here?

1585
01:59:09,584 --> 01:59:13,786
Manohar broke the promise he
made to Parvati during marriage.

1586
01:59:13,843 --> 01:59:17,161
Because of this his studies
and family is destroying.

1587
01:59:17,283 --> 01:59:18,396
What?

1588
01:59:19,267 --> 01:59:21,652
How many people do you
have in your family?

1589
01:59:21,874 --> 01:59:23,249
Eight of them including my mom.

1590
01:59:23,531 --> 01:59:25,729
Eight. How do you manage
your food everyday?

1591
01:59:26,169 --> 01:59:29,345
The Rs 3 you give, we
manage to get something.

1592
01:59:29,528 --> 01:59:30,879
Just Rs 3?

1593
01:59:30,901 --> 01:59:33,583
Nowadays, in Rs 3 not a single
person can eat properly.

1594
01:59:33,635 --> 01:59:35,168
How can eight people eat?

1595
01:59:35,191 --> 01:59:36,509
You are a strange man.

1596
01:59:36,804 --> 01:59:39,439
Anyway, first let's get
some food for the kids.

1597
01:59:39,495 --> 01:59:42,105
Then we will think about your
studies. - Come, Asha.

1598
01:59:54,117 --> 01:59:56,601
What are you looking at?
Help me out.

1599
02:00:06,939 --> 02:00:10,151
Are you asking me the amount?
I am selling anything. Where's your mom?

1600
02:00:11,930 --> 02:00:15,359
You might not get anything to
eat but you know to dance.

1601
02:00:15,531 --> 02:00:16,923
I am asking where is your mom.

1602
02:00:18,454 --> 02:00:21,318
You wish to answer this
also using dance moves.

1603
02:00:28,209 --> 02:00:30,855
Ratan, what are you doing here?
- Thank God you are here.

1604
02:00:30,982 --> 02:00:34,894
Why didn't you tell me that a strange
girl roams about in your house?

1605
02:00:35,036 --> 02:00:38,435
She was shouting so much...
- Ratan, don't you know.

1606
02:00:38,533 --> 02:00:40,800
No.
- She is my sister, Kamla.

1607
02:00:41,352 --> 02:00:42,863
She is dumb.
- Dumb?

1608
02:00:43,847 --> 02:00:45,139
Oh!

1609
02:00:47,149 --> 02:00:51,249
I am sorry. Whatever I
said was unknowingly.

1610
02:00:51,495 --> 02:00:53,840
It was my mistake.
I hope you have forgiven me.

1611
02:00:57,263 --> 02:00:58,811
Greetings!
- Greetings!

1612
02:00:59,638 --> 02:01:01,283
Suresh, who are they?

1613
02:01:01,357 --> 02:01:03,487
Ma'am, I am Vibhishan.

1614
02:01:03,619 --> 02:01:07,971
She is my sister. And my
elder brother is Ravana.

1615
02:01:11,980 --> 02:01:14,427
Where is this procession going?

1616
02:01:14,593 --> 02:01:17,742
They are my sisters.
- All of them are your sisters?

1617
02:01:18,270 --> 02:01:20,872
Ma'am, there is nothing
to worry about.

1618
02:01:20,980 --> 02:01:22,878
You can consider me as
your family member.

1619
02:01:23,015 --> 02:01:24,855
Take a look. We have got
all the grains possible.

1620
02:01:25,169 --> 02:01:27,700
Now no need to suffer.
Please cook something.

1621
02:01:27,788 --> 02:01:29,831
Today, even I will eat here itself.

1622
02:01:29,854 --> 02:01:32,922
Please come. Come. Let's cook fast.

1623
02:01:36,509 --> 02:01:39,369
Parvati's husband's younger sister.

1624
02:01:39,578 --> 02:01:42,416
What is she asking? - You are standing
quietly since you have come.

1625
02:01:42,512 --> 02:01:44,878
She is asking whether
you can talk or not.

1626
02:01:48,036 --> 02:01:49,972
Asha, you had said two things.

1627
02:01:50,029 --> 02:01:52,550
One was the food necessities
of this house. What's next?

1628
02:01:52,883 --> 02:01:53,982
Come here.

1629
02:01:56,587 --> 02:01:58,570
Now come with me and tell Parvati..

1630
02:01:58,621 --> 02:02:01,361
..that you have taken the responsibility
of this family from now on.

1631
02:02:01,430 --> 02:02:04,033
And somehow manage to help
Suresh finish his studies.

1632
02:02:04,207 --> 02:02:07,274
She keeps crying all day and
night as she is worried.

1633
02:02:07,555 --> 02:02:09,033
She has stopped eating as well.

1634
02:02:12,203 --> 02:02:14,063
What is this, mother?
- Have it, dear.

1635
02:02:14,637 --> 02:02:17,858
Have some.
- No, mother. I am not hungry.

1636
02:02:17,939 --> 02:02:20,489
You are lying.
You are lying, Parvati.

1637
02:02:20,826 --> 02:02:24,294
You are dealing with a monster.
What better can happen?

1638
02:02:24,543 --> 02:02:26,469
You will have to suffer.

1639
02:02:26,835 --> 02:02:30,470
Look, your kids are sitting with you.

1640
02:02:30,629 --> 02:02:33,997
Look at them.
Have something for them, dear.

1641
02:02:34,215 --> 02:02:36,400
Eat something.
I'll get water for you.

1642
02:02:40,630 --> 02:02:43,441
Mom, why are you sad?

1643
02:02:43,718 --> 02:02:46,202
I am not.
- Don't worry, mom.

1644
02:02:46,224 --> 02:02:48,441
When I grow up, I will earn a lot.

1645
02:02:48,535 --> 02:02:49,688
I will make sure uncle studies.

1646
02:02:49,786 --> 02:02:51,662
I will take care of you as well.

1647
02:02:53,910 --> 02:02:56,362
I'll feed you, mom.
You will eat, won't you?

1648
02:03:14,237 --> 02:03:18,364
Parvati, I thought that I will
feed you with my own hands.

1649
02:03:18,544 --> 02:03:20,434
But these have done it.

1650
02:03:21,162 --> 02:03:23,172
When these kids love you so much..

1651
02:03:23,541 --> 02:03:25,352
..then why are you sad?

1652
02:03:27,747 --> 02:03:30,671
Parvati, don't you
consider us as your own?

1653
02:03:31,381 --> 02:03:32,709
Then wipe your tears.

1654
02:03:33,724 --> 02:03:37,481
So what if Manohar has gone back
on his words? I am still alive.

1655
02:03:38,141 --> 02:03:40,504
Parvati, I visited your family.

1656
02:03:40,878 --> 02:03:44,504
Yes. And I have taken up the
responsibility of your family on me.

1657
02:03:44,785 --> 02:03:49,352
As far as Suresh is concerned, I will
make sure he completes his studies.

1658
02:03:49,578 --> 02:03:50,829
Hey cabbie!

1659
02:03:53,074 --> 02:03:55,583
What did you say?
You will make him a doctor!

1660
02:03:55,622 --> 02:03:56,692
Can you do it?

1661
02:03:57,164 --> 02:03:59,235
What do you have?
- What do you have?

1662
02:03:59,317 --> 02:04:01,301
I have a lot of money in many banks.

1663
02:04:01,379 --> 02:04:04,566
I have wealth. - If you have wealth,
I have determination.

1664
02:04:04,680 --> 02:04:08,065
If a man doesn't have anything,
how will determination help?

1665
02:04:08,117 --> 02:04:12,017
C'mon! Anything earned with
determination will remain for ages.

1666
02:04:12,044 --> 02:04:14,603
While the wealth you are talking
about will vanish soon.

1667
02:04:14,796 --> 02:04:16,994
I will make sure he becomes a doctor.
Not just that.

1668
02:04:17,090 --> 02:04:19,267
I will get Asha married
to him as well.

1669
02:04:19,379 --> 02:04:22,084
I see. So this is what
you are thinking.

1670
02:04:22,166 --> 02:04:26,367
I don't just think. Whatever I think
is what I will eventually do.

1671
02:04:26,509 --> 02:04:30,062
I would've done this long back
but Parvati came in between.

1672
02:04:30,087 --> 02:04:34,574
She wants him to become a doctor
first that's why I am not insisting.

1673
02:04:34,651 --> 02:04:37,936
First, let him become a doctor.
Then we'll see.

1674
02:04:37,987 --> 02:04:40,603
Do you money to make him a ward boy?

1675
02:04:40,646 --> 02:04:43,807
Whether I have money or not,
if I fail to help him become a doctor..

1676
02:04:43,900 --> 02:04:45,404
..then I won't ever
show my face to you.

1677
02:04:45,426 --> 02:04:48,594
Get lost! Let's see what you can do.

1678
02:04:52,266 --> 02:04:55,668
Greetings, sir.
- Greetings, Ratanlal. How are you?

1679
02:04:55,750 --> 02:04:58,282
I am fine. How are you?
- I am fine.

1680
02:04:58,344 --> 02:05:00,712
Sir, the car you had
given to me..

1681
02:05:00,753 --> 02:05:03,317
..thanks to the almighty
its running well.

1682
02:05:03,602 --> 02:05:06,925
Please keep this month's amount. Rs 200.
- What's the hurry?

1683
02:05:07,023 --> 02:05:08,907
There's a reason, sir.
- What's that?

1684
02:05:09,164 --> 02:05:11,551
Sir, I need Rs 1000 by
10th of this month.

1685
02:05:11,649 --> 02:05:14,581
Will you be able to help?
- You belong to a rich family.

1686
02:05:14,818 --> 02:05:18,453
When I was able to give you a car worth
Rs 15,000, then why not Rs 1000?

1687
02:05:18,578 --> 02:05:20,638
When do you need it?
- Right now if possible.

1688
02:05:20,661 --> 02:05:23,171
Right now? I don't
have any money now.

1689
02:05:23,639 --> 02:05:25,519
Do one thing. Come on the 7th.

1690
02:05:25,598 --> 02:05:27,738
Rs 1000 is nothing.
I can give you more.

1691
02:05:27,778 --> 02:05:31,277
No sir. I don't need
to build a college.

1692
02:05:31,375 --> 02:05:33,214
I needed the money to
get a boy educated.

1693
02:05:33,265 --> 02:05:35,118
Come on the 7th.
I will give it to you.

1694
02:05:35,200 --> 02:05:36,348
Sure?
- Absolutely!

1695
02:05:36,431 --> 02:05:37,857
Don't forget.
- I will surely give you.

1696
02:05:37,928 --> 02:05:39,491
Alright. Thank you.

1697
02:05:44,319 --> 02:05:47,143
Whether I have money or not, if I
fail to help him become a doctor..

1698
02:05:47,261 --> 02:05:48,899
..then I won't ever
show my face to you.

1699
02:05:53,963 --> 02:05:55,207
Greetings, sir.

1700
02:05:55,603 --> 02:05:58,752
Greetings.
- Today is 7th. Give me the money.

1701
02:05:59,612 --> 02:06:03,257
I am asking for money and you
are giving me the newspaper.

1702
02:06:03,380 --> 02:06:05,582
First read what is written
in the newspaper.

1703
02:06:05,623 --> 02:06:07,902
I don't have time to
read the newspaper, sir.

1704
02:06:07,988 --> 02:06:10,597
Please give me the money, I need to
meet the principal of the college.

1705
02:06:10,774 --> 02:06:13,886
Your brother has given an
advertisement in the newspaper.

1706
02:06:13,986 --> 02:06:16,465
Manohar? Advertisement?
- Yes. Read it.

1707
02:06:16,932 --> 02:06:19,379
'This is to inform
everyone that I have..'

1708
02:06:19,451 --> 02:06:21,679
'..earned all my wealth
through hard work.'

1709
02:06:21,812 --> 02:06:23,281
What a lie!

1710
02:06:24,159 --> 02:06:27,239
'My brother or sister
or any other relative..'

1711
02:06:27,340 --> 02:06:29,862
'..take any kind of loan
from anyone using my name..'

1712
02:06:30,025 --> 02:06:32,370
'..then it won't be
my responsibility.'

1713
02:06:32,449 --> 02:06:33,665
'Manoharlal.'

1714
02:06:33,717 --> 02:06:36,087
Forget about my brother, you
please give me the money.

1715
02:06:36,169 --> 02:06:41,372
Forgive me. I have been lending money
to you because of your brother.

1716
02:06:41,611 --> 02:06:44,076
Get an agreement from
him and take the money.

1717
02:06:44,108 --> 02:06:47,692
Agreement? Neither am I going to
ask and nor will he give it to me.

1718
02:06:47,744 --> 02:06:48,885
Then even I can't give you.

1719
02:06:48,967 --> 02:06:51,750
Don't joke, sir.
Please give me the money.

1720
02:06:51,802 --> 02:06:54,082
I am not joking.
Now listen to me carefully.

1721
02:06:54,324 --> 02:06:58,801
The loan amount that you give me
every month, if you ever become late..

1722
02:06:58,988 --> 02:07:01,045
..I will seize your car.

1723
02:07:01,087 --> 02:07:03,657
If I am unable to give it
then you can seize it.

1724
02:07:03,770 --> 02:07:05,770
But please give me Rs 1000 now.

1725
02:07:06,413 --> 02:07:08,897
Sir, if you don't help
me with this money..

1726
02:07:09,028 --> 02:07:11,224
..then a poor boy will not be
able to complete his studies.

1727
02:07:11,904 --> 02:07:13,278
Please look at me, sir.

1728
02:07:13,550 --> 02:07:17,777
Sir. Really?
Are you promises so fragile?

1729
02:07:17,876 --> 02:07:19,642
You asked me to come on the 7th.

1730
02:07:19,901 --> 02:07:22,131
After all you have
showed your true colors.

1731
02:07:26,597 --> 02:07:29,467
Have you read this?
If I give you a loan..

1732
02:07:29,593 --> 02:07:31,333
..then your brother will
lose his cool on me.

1733
02:07:31,569 --> 02:07:34,052
I am helpless. Forgive me. Bye.

1734
02:07:38,041 --> 02:07:40,911
Where is Ratan, Suresh?
- He said he will come with the money.

1735
02:07:41,112 --> 02:07:43,601
Today is 7th. Hasn't it
arranged for the money yet?

1736
02:07:43,687 --> 02:07:46,329
The money is arranged that's why
he has gone to get the money.

1737
02:07:47,032 --> 02:07:48,127
There he is.

1738
02:07:50,059 --> 02:07:51,470
Did you get the money, Ratan?

1739
02:07:55,975 --> 02:07:59,067
Tell me. Did you get the money?

1740
02:07:59,279 --> 02:08:00,427
Look at this.

1741
02:08:01,103 --> 02:08:05,097
Manohar has posted this on the
newspaper. Who will give us money now?

1742
02:08:05,368 --> 02:08:07,555
The lenders who were
ready to give money..

1743
02:08:07,672 --> 02:08:09,744
..aren't ready to pay a penny
because of this advertisement.

1744
02:08:10,476 --> 02:08:13,698
Whoever I went to ask for money, 
he got me out from there.

1745
02:08:14,317 --> 02:08:17,503
That's fine brother, 
but we should do something.

1746
02:08:17,646 --> 02:08:19,503
Only two days left for college to start.

1747
02:08:19,687 --> 02:08:21,791
So tell him to jump over
the wall and enter the college.

1748
02:08:21,995 --> 02:08:24,280
What nonsense ? 
- Now you tell me what should I do?

1749
02:08:24,630 --> 02:08:26,812
I am very angry on brother.
- Listen!

1750
02:08:27,713 --> 02:08:29,347
It's not your brother's fault.

1751
02:08:30,235 --> 02:08:31,677
My fate is to be blamed.

1752
02:08:31,729 --> 02:08:34,656
Fate on your forehead
not in the newspaper.

1753
02:08:34,712 --> 02:08:36,016
Why drag your fate in it?

1754
02:08:36,392 --> 02:08:37,943
Of course it is.

1755
02:08:38,412 --> 02:08:39,911
I am really unfortunate.

1756
02:08:40,434 --> 02:08:43,005
I think I am destined in
not becoming a doctor.

1757
02:08:43,736 --> 02:08:45,325
It's the final year of my studies.

1758
02:08:45,815 --> 02:08:48,342
My sister had faith on a lender.

1759
02:08:48,741 --> 02:08:50,445
Even he couldn't pay her.

1760
02:08:50,958 --> 02:08:54,589
After that my sister sacrificed
her happiness for my studies.

1761
02:08:55,099 --> 02:08:57,403
Such a huge sacrifice couldn't
help me finish my studies..

1762
02:08:57,508 --> 02:08:59,649
..how will anyone's sacrifice
help me in anyway?

1763
02:08:59,844 --> 02:09:02,061
Forget it. Forget everything.

1764
02:09:02,355 --> 02:09:03,938
Now nothing can happen.

1765
02:09:04,096 --> 02:09:07,632
Whether it is possible or not,
leave that to us.

1766
02:09:08,229 --> 02:09:10,130
Ratan, come here.

1767
02:09:17,980 --> 02:09:21,686
Why, Ratan? Why are you
quiet listening to me?

1768
02:09:23,839 --> 02:09:26,082
We don't have any other way, Ratan.

1769
02:09:27,879 --> 02:09:30,042
If you agree then I'll go.

1770
02:09:30,305 --> 02:09:31,404
Else, I won't.

1771
02:09:33,085 --> 02:09:34,581
What are you thinking, Ratan?

1772
02:09:35,684 --> 02:09:37,521
Okay. Alright.

1773
02:09:38,353 --> 02:09:42,217
After all you are going there with the
idea of helping him in his studies.

1774
02:09:43,492 --> 02:09:46,789
No problem. Go.

1775
02:09:54,535 --> 02:09:56,237
Come, sir. Come.

1776
02:09:56,508 --> 02:09:58,193
Hello!
- Good evening, sir.

1777
02:09:58,260 --> 02:10:00,104
Good morning. Good morning.

1778
02:10:00,184 --> 02:10:02,772
Sir, why don't you come
to our hotel these days?

1779
02:10:03,662 --> 02:10:05,618
What's the use of
coming to your hotel?

1780
02:10:05,956 --> 02:10:08,135
Your hotel doesn't serve drinks.

1781
02:10:08,215 --> 02:10:11,336
What do you want, sir?
Tea, coffee, cold drinks, juices?

1782
02:10:11,409 --> 02:10:14,813
Do human beings drink these things?

1783
02:10:14,859 --> 02:10:17,991
I have already had what I want.

1784
02:10:18,049 --> 02:10:20,497
In fact I have some as well. See.

1785
02:10:21,804 --> 02:10:25,602
Keep it inside. The police might come.
- Why? Are you afraid?

1786
02:10:25,908 --> 02:10:29,809
Idiot! I am a permit holder.
Understood?

1787
02:10:34,017 --> 02:10:35,747
Who is this girl?

1788
02:10:41,732 --> 02:10:42,783
Good.

1789
02:10:42,931 --> 02:10:46,967
Has she come here alone?
- I am seeing her for the first time.

1790
02:10:47,277 --> 02:10:50,795
She is new here.
- Really? Go and find out about her.

1791
02:10:51,017 --> 02:10:52,683
No sir, I can't do this.

1792
02:10:52,804 --> 02:10:55,431
If my manager learns
about, I will lose my job.

1793
02:10:55,567 --> 02:10:59,660
First, listen to what I
want you to find out.

1794
02:10:59,838 --> 02:11:03,194
Find out whether she has
come here to have tea..

1795
02:11:03,298 --> 02:11:06,500
..or have food or to make a call.

1796
02:11:06,611 --> 02:11:09,856
Can't you find that out?
- Yes, I can.

1797
02:11:10,284 --> 02:11:13,721
What do you think?
- I thought something else.

1798
02:11:15,248 --> 02:11:17,874
What's the need of this?
- Go. Hurry up.

1799
02:11:31,199 --> 02:11:34,544
Sir, you were right.
She comes here for money.

1800
02:11:34,570 --> 02:11:36,202
Oh! Very good.

1801
02:11:36,292 --> 02:11:39,353
She has connections with a rich man.
- Didn't I tell you?

1802
02:11:39,575 --> 02:11:41,461
Go and find out more about her.

1803
02:11:42,408 --> 02:11:47,852
She is coming here. Go and find out
about her. - No, sir. I can't.

1804
02:11:47,926 --> 02:11:51,188
I am going.
- He is going! Idiot!

1805
02:11:55,185 --> 02:11:57,154
Can I do anything for you?

1806
02:11:57,694 --> 02:12:01,623
Sorry. Ma'am. Please listen
to me, ma'am. Excuse me.

1807
02:12:01,662 --> 02:12:06,020
Idiot! You came in between.
Get out! Get out! Get out!

1808
02:12:08,785 --> 02:12:10,805
Ratan, why are you worried?
- Keep quiet.

1809
02:12:10,840 --> 02:12:12,529
Today is 9th and tomorrow is 10th.

1810
02:12:12,611 --> 02:12:14,577
Asha had gone to get money.
She hasn't come back yet.

1811
02:12:14,651 --> 02:12:16,584
I won't go back on my promise
that I made to Manohar.

1812
02:12:17,802 --> 02:12:21,384
There she is. Asha, have you
got the money? - Yes, Ratan.

1813
02:12:24,418 --> 02:12:25,980
Come. Sit in the car.

1814
02:12:38,683 --> 02:12:41,535
Go. Hurry up and submit your fees.
Some people are still going.

1815
02:12:41,591 --> 02:12:42,691
We have time.

1816
02:12:46,056 --> 02:12:47,876
A huge responsibility
has been taken care of.

1817
02:12:54,718 --> 02:12:55,540
Take it.

1818
02:12:59,875 --> 02:13:01,899
Hey. Come here.

1819
02:13:05,191 --> 02:13:06,807
Is this the way to serve milk?

1820
02:13:07,478 --> 02:13:08,744
Are you showing your anger?

1821
02:13:09,312 --> 02:13:12,074
A waiter from the hotel also
serves it with a smile.

1822
02:13:12,346 --> 02:13:14,986
Beloved wife, is this milk?

1823
02:13:15,469 --> 02:13:18,121
You have made your face as if
you have served poison to me.

1824
02:13:18,488 --> 02:13:22,104
Look, if you want to stay
with me then keep smiling.

1825
02:13:22,187 --> 02:13:26,644
Be happy. Else, I will leave
this house and go. I am serious.

1826
02:13:27,020 --> 02:13:30,694
What are you saying? Come here.
Sit down.

1827
02:13:31,871 --> 02:13:36,785
Tell me something. What has happened
that is making you so angry?

1828
02:13:37,281 --> 02:13:40,019
If I have made a mistake then
you should let me know of it.

1829
02:13:40,247 --> 02:13:42,594
You can correct me at any
given point of time.

1830
02:13:43,090 --> 02:13:45,735
Then I will do what
you ask me to do.

1831
02:13:46,072 --> 02:13:50,537
You never do that instead you are
saying that you will leave this house.

1832
02:13:51,081 --> 02:13:55,068
If you leave then
what will we do here?

1833
02:13:55,862 --> 02:13:59,060
If you talk to me like
this just once a day..

1834
02:13:59,090 --> 02:14:00,516
..then I will be so happy.

1835
02:14:01,340 --> 02:14:03,440
Here, have some milk.
- You have it.

1836
02:14:03,498 --> 02:14:06,752
You first. If you don't
have it then even I won't.

1837
02:14:08,090 --> 02:14:10,563
Manoharlal!
- Who is it?

1838
02:14:10,644 --> 02:14:12,895
Loser! Gooseberry!

1839
02:14:13,109 --> 02:14:15,998
I can see that you sitting at ease.
I hope you are alright.

1840
02:14:16,039 --> 02:14:19,260
Who are you? Get up! Who are you?
Where are you from? - What?

1841
02:14:21,272 --> 02:14:23,750
What is this, Manoharlal?
- You didn't recognise me?

1842
02:14:23,997 --> 02:14:27,788
5 years ago the two of us
together took big contracts.

1843
02:14:27,840 --> 02:14:29,599
We earned a lot of money.

1844
02:14:29,667 --> 02:14:34,306
We used to be together all the time.
Have you forgotten already?

1845
02:14:34,336 --> 02:14:36,218
Fine. What do you want now?

1846
02:14:36,315 --> 02:14:40,152
Me? I have come to fix the marriage
of my son and your sister.

1847
02:14:40,288 --> 02:14:44,749
I know you son. He keeps roaming
about the city in a drunk state.

1848
02:14:44,780 --> 02:14:47,522
You want my sister to get
married to a drunkard. No way!

1849
02:14:47,750 --> 02:14:51,714
He is young man.
He is bound to do such things.

1850
02:14:51,954 --> 02:14:54,475
Once he gets married, things
will fall in place for him.

1851
02:14:54,507 --> 02:14:57,854
Forget about him. First you tell
me when will you mend your ways?

1852
02:14:57,952 --> 02:15:00,466
What's the point of mending
our ways at this age?

1853
02:15:00,497 --> 02:15:05,243
You enter a gentleman's house, climb the
staircase without informing anyone.

1854
02:15:05,296 --> 02:15:09,268
You enter his bedroom without
even knocking like an illiterate.

1855
02:15:09,383 --> 02:15:13,772
Above it all, you want my
sister to my your son!

1856
02:15:13,784 --> 02:15:15,376
Get lost!
- C'mon!

1857
02:15:15,430 --> 02:15:16,733
Don't sit! Get up!

1858
02:15:17,396 --> 02:15:20,573
Manoharlal, remember one thing.

1859
02:15:20,921 --> 02:15:22,502
Even I am wealthy just like you.

1860
02:15:22,565 --> 02:15:25,689
Go and enjoy with your wealth.
Get out!

1861
02:15:25,952 --> 02:15:27,179
I am going.
- Go!

1862
02:15:27,345 --> 02:15:28,370
I am going.

1863
02:15:40,862 --> 02:15:45,663
Wow! The girl has come again.

1864
02:15:48,033 --> 02:15:53,961
Greetings! I have waiting for you.
Please say something. Listen. Listen!

1865
02:15:54,488 --> 02:15:58,799
Ma'am, please! She's gone. Gone.

1866
02:15:59,097 --> 02:16:02,437
She won't talk to me. Alright.

1867
02:16:04,671 --> 02:16:08,769
Take it, Ratan. - What is this?
Suresh gave his exams a month ago.

1868
02:16:08,848 --> 02:16:11,151
Why have you brought money then?
- How will his family survive?

1869
02:16:11,559 --> 02:16:14,928
Oh! So you are worried
about his family already!

1870
02:16:15,120 --> 02:16:17,880
I am right here and so is my cab.

1871
02:16:18,303 --> 02:16:21,967
Alright. No problem. Give.
- How did his exams go?

1872
02:16:22,118 --> 02:16:26,323
How would I know? He is right here.
Ask him yourself. - Go ahead.

1873
02:16:26,538 --> 02:16:29,084
My exams were good, Asha.
I will surely pass.

1874
02:16:29,166 --> 02:16:32,756
Ratan, as soon as his results are out,
I should be the first one to know.

1875
02:16:32,944 --> 02:16:36,212
Surely. But before Manohar
learns that you are here..

1876
02:16:36,391 --> 02:16:39,530
..please leave immediately. Go. Go on.

1877
02:16:41,486 --> 02:16:43,665
Ratan, the results will
be out in some time.

1878
02:16:43,754 --> 02:16:46,227
Why did you send her away then?
- You are very innocent.

1879
02:16:46,537 --> 02:16:48,924
In case, out of ill-fate you fail..

1880
02:16:49,193 --> 02:16:52,895
..then she would've been shattered.
She would've fainted here itself.

1881
02:16:52,943 --> 02:16:55,990
Do you get it?
The newspaper has come.

1882
02:16:57,604 --> 02:16:59,589
Wait! Give it to me!

1883
02:17:04,445 --> 02:17:07,679
Where is it? Where is it? Where is it?

1884
02:17:08,732 --> 02:17:10,070
Here it is!

1885
02:17:10,200 --> 02:17:13,196
1st Class! Take a look.
Wow, son. Great!

1886
02:17:14,508 --> 02:17:17,017
You did a fantastic job.
You have passed with first class.

1887
02:17:18,651 --> 02:17:21,885
Ratan, this has been
possible because of you.

1888
02:17:21,933 --> 02:17:24,584
C'mon! I did not write the exams.

1889
02:17:24,636 --> 02:17:28,334
Doctor Suresh, I have just kept
my promise unlike my brother.

1890
02:17:28,536 --> 02:17:30,772
Come. Let's inform Parvati first.
Come.

1891
02:17:31,781 --> 02:17:35,306
Parvati! Parvati! Parvati!
- What is it?

1892
02:17:35,438 --> 02:17:38,976
Parvati!
- Tell me, what is the matter?

1893
02:17:39,045 --> 02:17:41,410
Parvati, you will be so proud today.

1894
02:17:41,457 --> 02:17:43,144
Your wishes have come true.

1895
02:17:43,214 --> 02:17:46,172
Your brother... Come here.
He is a doctor now.

1896
02:17:46,299 --> 02:17:49,337
Take a look. His percentage is given.
Take a look.

1897
02:17:51,920 --> 02:17:55,713
Ratan, you helped my brother complete
his studies and not just that..

1898
02:17:56,255 --> 02:18:00,136
..you gave a life to
6 ill-fated girls.

1899
02:18:00,219 --> 02:18:02,239
It's because of your
blessings, Parvati.

1900
02:18:02,610 --> 02:18:05,458
Go and take her blessings. C'mon!

1901
02:18:08,016 --> 02:18:09,517
Suresh.
- Parvati.

1902
02:18:12,650 --> 02:18:15,076
Parvati, I need to talk to you
about something important.

1903
02:18:15,410 --> 02:18:18,949
He is a doctor now and can take care
of all problems, even heart problems.

1904
02:18:19,060 --> 02:18:21,475
Manohar has some
serious heart issues.

1905
02:18:21,537 --> 02:18:24,395
I mean he is stone-hearted.
Don't mind, Parvati.

1906
02:18:24,559 --> 02:18:28,699
Doctor Suresh, why don't you start
your practicing from Manohar. - Quiet.

1907
02:18:29,000 --> 02:18:31,429
If you say such things,
he will lose his cool.

1908
02:18:31,524 --> 02:18:33,210
Yes, I know my brother.

1909
02:18:33,256 --> 02:18:36,264
But today I will say what I have to.
- C'mon, doctor.

1910
02:18:36,838 --> 02:18:40,216
Brother.
- Hey, why are you shouting?

1911
02:18:40,269 --> 02:18:45,621
I am not shouting, my dear brother.
Remember, you had said one day.

1912
02:18:45,737 --> 02:18:49,069
What did you say then? That I won't
be able to fund his studies.

1913
02:18:49,250 --> 02:18:51,808
Take a close look. Today, I have
managed to helped him become a doctor.

1914
02:18:51,881 --> 02:18:54,448
MBBS. His percentage is here.
Take a look.

1915
02:18:54,763 --> 02:18:59,884
Don't be mad, brother. I have
come here with a good news.

1916
02:19:00,004 --> 02:19:03,168
Also, I would like to
request something to you.

1917
02:19:03,234 --> 02:19:05,823
Now get Asha and Suresh married.

1918
02:19:05,945 --> 02:19:08,327
This is so that you
don't feel left out.

1919
02:19:08,381 --> 02:19:10,897
Do you think I am ready
for this association?

1920
02:19:10,945 --> 02:19:13,143
Whether you agree or not, I am ready.

1921
02:19:13,167 --> 02:19:15,947
How will that help?
- Oh really!

1922
02:19:15,999 --> 02:19:18,338
They will become husband & wife.
- Come, doctor.

1923
02:19:29,130 --> 02:19:30,890
Listen. Come here.

1924
02:19:31,641 --> 02:19:36,881
The beggar Manoharlal must have
had food here so many times.

1925
02:19:37,043 --> 02:19:39,001
You must've served him as well.

1926
02:19:39,234 --> 02:19:42,473
Forget about it. For how long
will you keep cribbing about it?

1927
02:19:42,557 --> 02:19:44,631
What did you say? Am I cribbing?

1928
02:19:44,899 --> 02:19:48,330
Do you know what he said to me?
He called me an illiterate man!

1929
02:19:48,480 --> 02:19:50,488
Won't I feel bad about it?

1930
02:19:50,617 --> 02:19:52,138
Sir!
- Get lost!

1931
02:19:52,362 --> 02:19:54,064
Mr. Manoharlal has come.
- Who?

1932
02:19:54,128 --> 02:19:55,658
Mr. Manoharlal.
- Oh!

1933
02:19:56,353 --> 02:19:59,497
Mr. Manoharlal! God has sent him.

1934
02:19:59,807 --> 02:20:01,626
I will seek revenge.

1935
02:20:01,730 --> 02:20:05,319
Take these chairs away. Hurry up!

1936
02:20:06,355 --> 02:20:09,085
Listen, sit here.
- What are you doing?

1937
02:20:09,131 --> 02:20:11,559
Leave me.
- I said, sit here.

1938
02:20:13,554 --> 02:20:16,543
Listen! Go and send him inside.

1939
02:20:17,686 --> 02:20:19,889
Hurry up!
Let him come.

1940
02:20:21,778 --> 02:20:28,741
Greetings, Mr. Dinanath! Wow! What a
beautiful pair this is! - Who are you?

1941
02:20:29,145 --> 02:20:32,713
Aren't you able to see that a
husband and wife are sitting alone?

1942
02:20:32,871 --> 02:20:36,404
How dare you enter the room without
knocking like an illiterate?

1943
02:20:36,609 --> 02:20:38,151
Do you have any manners?

1944
02:20:38,289 --> 02:20:43,053
Mr. Dinanath, I know you are seeking
revenge for what I said that day.

1945
02:20:43,126 --> 02:20:47,902
The thing is that I had a small
argument with my wife that day.

1946
02:20:48,010 --> 02:20:49,864
That's why I lost my cool.

1947
02:20:49,928 --> 02:20:54,227
Everyone loses someone's cool but
that doesn't mean you speak rubbish.

1948
02:20:54,412 --> 02:20:58,022
That day it was my mistake.
But you are my friend.

1949
02:20:58,074 --> 02:21:00,263
If you don't forgive me, who will?

1950
02:21:00,402 --> 02:21:03,871
Listen, today I have come with a
suggestion. - What suggestion?

1951
02:21:04,122 --> 02:21:06,959
Get your son and my sister married.

1952
02:21:07,991 --> 02:21:10,588
Forget about the old tiffs.
Don't be mad.

1953
02:21:10,950 --> 02:21:16,139
Manoharlal, I wanted you to realise.
That's done.

1954
02:21:16,370 --> 02:21:17,911
Listen, get a chair.

1955
02:21:17,993 --> 02:21:22,070
There's no need for chair.
I am happy now. Let's go. - Where?

1956
02:21:22,124 --> 02:21:23,739
Let's begin with the preparations.

1957
02:21:23,781 --> 02:21:25,849
You are strange man.
It isn't my marriage

1958
02:21:25,932 --> 02:21:28,966
First, let the girl and boy meet.
- Get the boy along. Let's go.

1959
02:21:29,029 --> 02:21:30,881
My son isn't at home now.

1960
02:21:31,066 --> 02:21:35,068
I will get him to your house on an
auspicious day. - Don't forget.

1961
02:21:35,229 --> 02:21:37,802
Yes. - Ma'am, it seems he
is still a bit mad at me.

1962
02:21:37,884 --> 02:21:40,390
It would be your responsibility
to get him. I'll take your leave.

1963
02:21:41,311 --> 02:21:42,819
Asha!
- Yes, Manohar.

1964
02:21:42,901 --> 02:21:44,693
You will not go out
of house from now on.

1965
02:21:44,746 --> 02:21:46,975
If you do, you will
see the worst of me.

1966
02:21:51,920 --> 02:21:55,823
Driver! Where are you?
- I am here, sir. Please come.

1967
02:21:55,873 --> 02:21:59,453
Hey, what's this?
A cab always has 2 colors.

1968
02:21:59,533 --> 02:22:02,310
But yours is just one color.
- This is a private cab, sir.

1969
02:22:02,347 --> 02:22:05,018
This runs inside the city as
well as outside the city.

1970
02:22:05,108 --> 02:22:07,552
I have my license.
Please come and sit.

1971
02:22:07,684 --> 02:22:11,270
I asked you because we are going
to see a potential bride.

1972
02:22:11,360 --> 02:22:14,759
Oh! - If someone stops in the middle
of the road and creates a ruckus..

1973
02:22:14,836 --> 02:22:16,173
..we'll get worried unnecessarily.

1974
02:22:16,214 --> 02:22:17,528
There will be no problem, sir.

1975
02:22:17,605 --> 02:22:20,059
Whoever has traveled in it
to visit a potential bride..

1976
02:22:20,093 --> 02:22:23,275
..have got married happily.
Please come. There's nothing to worry.

1977
02:22:23,351 --> 02:22:24,633
That's great.

1978
02:22:31,160 --> 02:22:34,190
Gopal, behave yourself in front
of them. - Sir.

1979
02:22:34,414 --> 02:22:36,577
Have you come here to
meet a potential bride?

1980
02:22:36,635 --> 02:22:40,125
Why?
- Had you come in your own car..

1981
02:22:40,232 --> 02:22:41,893
..even then you wouldn't
have received any honor.

1982
02:22:41,931 --> 02:22:43,461
You have come here in a cab!

1983
02:22:43,731 --> 02:22:46,234
This house belongs to
a very rich man, sir.

1984
02:22:46,532 --> 02:22:49,161
Am I a poor man?
- No.

1985
02:22:49,363 --> 02:22:50,944
Both are equal.
- Isn't it?

1986
02:22:50,996 --> 02:22:51,964
Yes. Go on.

1987
02:22:52,261 --> 02:22:53,475
Come.

1988
02:22:55,204 --> 02:22:58,173
Hey, come. Sit down.

1989
02:22:58,896 --> 02:23:02,137
We thought you will be coming in
the morning. Anyway, no problem.

1990
02:23:02,237 --> 02:23:03,846
What would you like? Tea or coffee?

1991
02:23:03,898 --> 02:23:06,127
First, we wish to meet the girl.

1992
02:23:06,166 --> 02:23:08,926
Tea and coffee can be done later.
- Alright.

1993
02:23:09,013 --> 02:23:10,255
Mom!

1994
02:23:11,042 --> 02:23:13,344
Hey! Did he call you? Sit down!

1995
02:23:14,074 --> 02:23:17,343
Parvati, it is late. They are waiting.
Where is Asha?

1996
02:23:17,441 --> 02:23:19,476
Asha is coming.
- Yes, send her soon.

1997
02:23:20,965 --> 02:23:22,695
She is coming in sometime.
- No problem.

1998
02:23:22,794 --> 02:23:24,815
We thought you will be
coming in the morning.

1999
02:23:24,866 --> 02:23:27,445
That's why she got ready
in the morning itself.

2000
02:23:27,490 --> 02:23:30,645
When you didn't come, she changed.
Now she is getting ready again.

2001
02:23:30,727 --> 02:23:33,451
Oh! She is getting ready again.
- Yes, she is coming.

2002
02:23:33,534 --> 02:23:34,705
Okay.

2003
02:23:34,766 --> 02:23:37,056
C'mon. Wipe your tears.

2004
02:23:39,149 --> 02:23:40,321
Go on.

2005
02:23:42,931 --> 02:23:45,720
I would suggest let them get
married as soon as possible.

2006
02:23:45,802 --> 02:23:47,536
Find an auspicious time
in this week itself.

2007
02:23:47,554 --> 02:23:51,537
That's the reason I had come
to meet you the other day.

2008
02:23:51,958 --> 02:23:53,370
Forget about it.

2009
02:24:15,262 --> 02:24:16,873
Dad.
- What is it?

2010
02:24:17,056 --> 02:24:18,765
Is she the one?
- Yes.

2011
02:24:18,943 --> 02:24:20,458
Is she good?
- Yes.

2012
02:24:20,491 --> 02:24:22,413
Then what's the problem.
- Do you know who she is?

2013
02:24:22,448 --> 02:24:24,083
His sister.
- No. I am not saying that.

2014
02:24:24,165 --> 02:24:25,805
We will talk about all this at home.

2015
02:24:25,814 --> 02:24:29,602
So? I hope he likes her.
What is your son saying?

2016
02:24:29,702 --> 02:24:32,359
Nothing. He is asking
is she your sister?

2017
02:24:32,413 --> 02:24:34,929
Yes. Just get the auspicious
time for marriage fixed.

2018
02:24:34,951 --> 02:24:37,022
Let's get it done this week itself.
We'll take your leave...

2019
02:24:37,074 --> 02:24:39,712
Wait. Please have some tea.

2020
02:24:39,764 --> 02:24:42,916
Now we will have a
grand wedding feast.

2021
02:24:42,999 --> 02:24:44,699
Alright. No problem.

2022
02:24:45,181 --> 02:24:46,273
Greetings!
- Greetings!

2023
02:24:46,355 --> 02:24:47,125
Greetings!
- Greetings!

2024
02:24:47,150 --> 02:24:48,118
Let's go.

2025
02:24:52,473 --> 02:24:54,003
Ratan, won't win.

2026
02:24:54,570 --> 02:24:56,283
He was challenging me!

2027
02:24:57,143 --> 02:24:58,905
Dad. Dad, that girl...

2028
02:24:58,970 --> 02:25:01,872
Oh God! Why are you
irritating me so much?

2029
02:25:01,907 --> 02:25:03,672
I have fixed your marriage with her.

2030
02:25:03,695 --> 02:25:06,943
That's not the point. That girl goes
to the hotel and earns money often.

2031
02:25:06,974 --> 02:25:08,188
Shut up, idiot!

2032
02:25:08,269 --> 02:25:10,203
A rich man's sister
will go to the hotel!

2033
02:25:10,255 --> 02:25:13,284
I am telling the truth. I have seen
her in the hotel a lot of times.

2034
02:25:13,326 --> 02:25:15,858
You must have seen some other
girl in a drunk state.

2035
02:25:15,916 --> 02:25:17,702
Crazy fellow!

2036
02:25:17,878 --> 02:25:21,067
He is telling the truth.
- Shut up! What is right?

2037
02:25:21,161 --> 02:25:25,171
Don't be mad, sir.
Nothing is hidden from a cab driver.

2038
02:25:25,489 --> 02:25:28,722
I have seen her go
to the hotel myself.

2039
02:25:28,805 --> 02:25:30,700
What?
- Yes.

2040
02:25:30,949 --> 02:25:35,553
Manoharlal is such a creep.
So this is how he became a rich man!

2041
02:25:35,706 --> 02:25:37,825
Do you still want to get
your son married to her?

2042
02:25:37,877 --> 02:25:40,054
Reverse the cab.
- That's a like a man!

2043
02:25:41,272 --> 02:25:43,975
Manoharlal! Manoharlal!

2044
02:25:43,997 --> 02:25:46,028
Please come. What happened?

2045
02:25:46,109 --> 02:25:49,850
You have come back.
Is the date fixed? - Shut up!

2046
02:25:50,003 --> 02:25:54,444
After seeing what your sister does,
no one would want to marry her.

2047
02:25:54,566 --> 02:25:56,410
What nonsense are you talking about?

2048
02:25:56,493 --> 02:25:58,155
Are you trying to fool us?

2049
02:25:58,237 --> 02:25:59,840
Am I fooling you? Really!

2050
02:25:59,900 --> 02:26:02,407
Yes, you are.
You pretend to be a rich man!

2051
02:26:02,621 --> 02:26:06,776
When I came home to talk about your
sister's marriage with my son..

2052
02:26:06,856 --> 02:26:09,209
..you insulted me and
asked me to leave.

2053
02:26:09,291 --> 02:26:13,004
Then you came to my house asking
to consider the alliance.

2054
02:26:13,074 --> 02:26:16,786
I knew it that moment
that something is wrong.

2055
02:26:16,997 --> 02:26:19,523
What's wrong?
What nonsense are you talking?

2056
02:26:19,635 --> 02:26:24,162
Am I? Your sister goes to the
hotel to earn money. Yes or no?

2057
02:26:24,221 --> 02:26:26,358
What did you say? Get out of here!

2058
02:26:26,396 --> 02:26:30,770
Now that the truth is out,
you are getting wild! - Get out!

2059
02:26:31,076 --> 02:26:33,828
A rich man's sister doesn't
need to do that. - Rubbish!

2060
02:26:33,917 --> 02:26:39,366
Rich man! Not just once, my son has
seen your sister a lot of times there.

2061
02:26:39,420 --> 02:26:41,332
Your son is not truthful either.

2062
02:26:41,371 --> 02:26:44,435
Not just him.
Even the cab driver said so.

2063
02:26:44,489 --> 02:26:46,980
Which driver? - He is waiting outside.
Call him and ask.

2064
02:26:47,054 --> 02:26:48,283
Driver!

2065
02:26:56,482 --> 02:26:58,201
Oh! It's you!

2066
02:26:59,797 --> 02:27:03,499
So you are doing this so
that they don't get married!

2067
02:27:05,530 --> 02:27:07,868
Hey!
- It is true.

2068
02:27:08,680 --> 02:27:10,294
Asha used to go to the hotel.

2069
02:27:10,540 --> 02:27:13,404
Now what do you have to say?
- Shut up!

2070
02:27:13,705 --> 02:27:16,902
Hey!
- I am telling the truth.

2071
02:27:16,930 --> 02:27:21,315
So, our sister Asha used to go to
the hotel! - Why don't you ask her?

2072
02:27:21,430 --> 02:27:22,967
What if she refuses?

2073
02:27:23,023 --> 02:27:25,462
First, call her and ask.
- What is she refuses?

2074
02:27:25,566 --> 02:27:27,963
Then I will kill myself.
- Asha!

2075
02:27:32,568 --> 02:27:34,280
Did you go to the hotel?
- Yes.

2076
02:27:35,322 --> 02:27:37,133
Why did you go?
- For money.

2077
02:27:37,211 --> 02:27:38,466
For money!

2078
02:27:39,759 --> 02:27:42,325
First, ask her why she needed money.

2079
02:27:42,445 --> 02:27:44,215
Then you can do what you want.
Ask her.

2080
02:27:44,473 --> 02:27:46,125
Why did you need money?

2081
02:27:46,472 --> 02:27:49,265
To help Suresh finish his studies.
- You went to the hotel for that!

2082
02:27:49,327 --> 02:27:51,410
Is it right for a girl to
go to the hotel like that?

2083
02:27:51,505 --> 02:27:54,210
Was it right for you to promise a poor
family and go back on your words?

2084
02:27:54,440 --> 02:27:56,441
Shut up! Else...
- I won't keep quiet!

2085
02:27:56,479 --> 02:27:59,205
Suresh wasn't able to study because
you went back on your words.

2086
02:27:59,274 --> 02:28:01,416
His family couldn't survive.

2087
02:28:01,845 --> 02:28:05,306
Thanks to our sister that Suresh was
able to complete his final year.

2088
02:28:05,364 --> 02:28:08,898
Because of that his family
will be able to survive.

2089
02:28:08,977 --> 02:28:11,848
Ratan, she went to the
hotel for a dumb girl.

2090
02:28:12,020 --> 02:28:13,891
She went there for 6 helpless kids.

2091
02:28:14,350 --> 02:28:18,005
Why? Why will our
sister go to the hotel..

2092
02:28:18,123 --> 02:28:20,059
..to feed an unknown family?

2093
02:28:20,166 --> 02:28:24,517
Not just for that, she completed a
responsibility you had taken up.

2094
02:28:24,678 --> 02:28:27,903
So, it is true that you
went to the hotel.

2095
02:28:28,358 --> 02:28:30,085
That too for money.

2096
02:28:30,267 --> 02:28:33,579
Not for money, Manohar.
For Suresh's studies.

2097
02:28:34,176 --> 02:28:36,509
How dare you do something like that?

2098
02:28:36,597 --> 02:28:38,866
One needs to be courageous
to be able to do good.

2099
02:28:38,927 --> 02:28:41,625
So, you knew that she
went to the hotel!

2100
02:28:41,715 --> 02:28:43,959
What do you mean?
I was the one to send her there.

2101
02:28:44,661 --> 02:28:46,717
Idiotic girl! Go and die!

2102
02:28:48,524 --> 02:28:51,274
Did you really go?
- Yes, I did.

2103
02:28:51,292 --> 02:28:54,146
You did! Idiotic girl!
Shameless woman!

2104
02:28:54,261 --> 02:28:56,699
You have defamed our family.

2105
02:28:56,912 --> 02:29:00,649
Had you died for Suresh's
studies, I would've been happier.

2106
02:29:00,795 --> 02:29:03,014
Shameless! Die!

2107
02:29:03,399 --> 02:29:07,214
How can you be so shameless to say
that you went to a hotel to earn?

2108
02:29:07,305 --> 02:29:10,013
How dare you! How dare you!
How dare you!

2109
02:29:10,121 --> 02:29:11,577
Parvati! Listen to me.

2110
02:29:11,629 --> 02:29:15,444
What is left to be heard?
You were the one who sent her there.

2111
02:29:15,572 --> 02:29:17,297
Yes, I did.

2112
02:29:17,361 --> 02:29:21,086
Shameless! You sent a
girl to the hotel.

2113
02:29:21,176 --> 02:29:24,486
You sent your sister to the hotel!

2114
02:29:24,569 --> 02:29:27,406
Yes, I sent my sister to the hotel.

2115
02:29:27,608 --> 02:29:30,257
You did! You did! You did!
- Parvati!

2116
02:29:30,928 --> 02:29:32,995
Even you had been to the hotel once.
Right?

2117
02:29:40,569 --> 02:29:41,986
Why are you quiet now?

2118
02:29:42,398 --> 02:29:45,162
All the girls who go to the
hotel don't always do wrong.

2119
02:29:45,554 --> 02:29:48,151
Do you really think Asha
will do something like that?

2120
02:29:48,426 --> 02:29:50,014
Had she done anything wrong..

2121
02:29:50,094 --> 02:29:52,026
..do you think I would've been
standing here alive in front of you?

2122
02:29:52,210 --> 02:29:54,312
This great man standing here.
My brother.

2123
02:29:54,390 --> 02:29:56,797
I had to lie so that he
realizes his mistakes.

2124
02:29:57,210 --> 02:29:58,668
Lie!
- Yes, Parvati.

2125
02:29:59,065 --> 02:30:00,734
You just beat us up really quick.

2126
02:30:01,525 --> 02:30:04,662
Parvati, you were in love
with someone, right?

2127
02:30:06,080 --> 02:30:09,346
Do you know that he was fighting a
case for the wealth worth Rs 4,00,000?

2128
02:30:10,139 --> 02:30:13,851
Do you know that he had won that
case and he got that money?

2129
02:30:14,492 --> 02:30:17,278
Do you know that he made
a hotel from that money?

2130
02:30:17,617 --> 02:30:19,651
Do you know that this
is the same hotel?

2131
02:30:20,376 --> 02:30:23,463
No. - Then you don't
know us either, Parvati.

2132
02:30:24,083 --> 02:30:29,039
Parvati, he met Asha one day and
asked her about you and Suresh.

2133
02:30:29,096 --> 02:30:33,623
He had asked her to inform him
if we ever needed his help.

2134
02:30:33,702 --> 02:30:37,951
He said if he was able to help,
he would be more than happy.

2135
02:30:38,028 --> 02:30:39,587
Asha told me about it.

2136
02:30:39,878 --> 02:30:44,669
When we desperately needed money,
I asked her to get the money.

2137
02:30:45,061 --> 02:30:47,935
He isn't an unknown person.
We would've returned the money.

2138
02:30:48,153 --> 02:30:50,413
That's when Asha went to the
hotel and got the money.

2139
02:30:50,574 --> 02:30:53,168
Even mom knew about it.
- Mom!

2140
02:30:53,927 --> 02:30:57,807
What is it?
- Mother, what is all this?

2141
02:30:57,817 --> 02:31:00,583
Yes, dear. I agreed to it.

2142
02:31:01,202 --> 02:31:02,938
Nothing is wrong in this.

2143
02:31:03,234 --> 02:31:07,174
I did this to make him
realise that he is wrong.

2144
02:31:07,344 --> 02:31:11,157
I agreed to this so that
this family is happy.

2145
02:31:11,933 --> 02:31:15,112
Parvati, you are so pious and pure.

2146
02:31:15,494 --> 02:31:18,598
A girl from the family that you are in
can never do anything wrong.

2147
02:31:19,236 --> 02:31:21,803
Can Asha do anything wrong?

2148
02:31:28,056 --> 02:31:31,310
Manoharlal, stop!
Stop it, Manoharlal!

2149
02:31:31,449 --> 02:31:33,757
Let me die!
- Stop it! Stop!

2150
02:31:33,848 --> 02:31:37,199
Wait! Stop!
- I have committed a sin.

2151
02:31:37,332 --> 02:31:39,202
I doubted my own sister.

2152
02:31:39,294 --> 02:31:42,206
Not just you, even we
did so, Manoharlal.

2153
02:31:42,273 --> 02:31:45,008
But now that we know the
truth, we have learnt..

2154
02:31:45,270 --> 02:31:47,007
..that your sister is a gem.

2155
02:31:47,029 --> 02:31:49,371
I am ashamed of myself.

2156
02:31:50,226 --> 02:31:52,420
If possible, please forgive me.
- What are you doing?

2157
02:31:52,460 --> 02:31:53,933
Let go of me.

2158
02:32:00,861 --> 02:32:03,337
Suresh, please forgive me.

2159
02:32:04,038 --> 02:32:05,640
Come. Come here.

2160
02:32:08,748 --> 02:32:10,748
Always be happy.
- Wow!

2161
02:32:10,912 --> 02:32:14,014
Whatever God does is for the good.

2162
02:32:22,302 --> 02:32:25,399
You are behind all the good
things that happened to me.

2163
02:32:25,928 --> 02:32:30,167
I just learnt that you helped my
brother complete his studies.

2164
02:32:30,766 --> 02:32:33,828
I will always remember your favors.

2165
02:32:33,968 --> 02:32:38,113
Parvati, I am not here to
hear good things about me.

2166
02:32:38,992 --> 02:32:41,736
I have come here to ask
something from you.

2167
02:32:41,849 --> 02:32:44,474
What?
- I hope you won't refuse.

2168
02:32:44,623 --> 02:32:47,431
If I am able to give you,
I definitely will.

2169
02:32:47,599 --> 02:32:50,177
First, tell me that
you have forgiven me.

2170
02:32:50,376 --> 02:32:51,777
Forgiveness? For what?

2171
02:32:52,095 --> 02:32:55,299
I hope you remember,
you had asked me..

2172
02:32:55,828 --> 02:32:59,510
..to get married to someone
and be happy. - Yes.

2173
02:32:59,906 --> 02:33:03,585
After a long time, I really liked
a girl and I got married to her.

2174
02:33:03,669 --> 02:33:07,212
Really? Why did you have
to apologise for that?

2175
02:33:07,313 --> 02:33:10,562
I got married without informing you.
That's why.

2176
02:33:10,846 --> 02:33:12,506
I have got my wife along.

2177
02:33:13,173 --> 02:33:15,022
Where is she?
- Wait.

2178
02:33:16,343 --> 02:33:17,477
I'll get her.

2179
02:33:23,572 --> 02:33:24,829
Kamla!

2180
02:33:31,107 --> 02:33:33,289
Sir, you are great!

2181
02:33:33,358 --> 02:33:35,396
May God always bless you.

2182
02:33:36,160 --> 02:33:38,991
Mr. Dinanath, don't you wish to go back?
The cab meter is on.

2183
02:33:39,031 --> 02:33:42,028
Let's go. Let's go.
- I don't sit in cabs much.

2184
02:33:42,068 --> 02:33:44,379
I had to sit today because of him.
